NK035(ci)004:1261: rnams kyi phung po lnga dag par byed pa'i don
NK035(ci)004:1262: du phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan pa nyid
NK035(ci)004:1263: yin na de yang ston pa phun sum tshogs pa
NK035(ci)004:1264: rdo rje 'chang chen po des yul dga' ldan brtsegs
NK035(ci)004:1265: par gnas phun tshogs pa me tog pad+ma'i steng du
NK035(ci)004:1266: ston pa khye'u snang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pas
NK035(ci)004:1267: 'khor sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis la bstan pa rgyud
NK035(ci)004:1268: thams cad snga ba bstan pa kun gyi rtsa ba
NK035(ci)004:1269: sgra thal 'gyur gsungs rgyud kyi sdud pa po ni
NK035(ci)004:1270: lha'i bu dga' byed dbang phyug gis mdzad grogs ni
NK035(ci)004:1271: lha'i bu nyi ma rab tu snang byed la sogs
NK035(ci)004:1272: pa dus tshe lo dpag tu med pa'i dus na'o
NK035(ci)004:1273: gnyis pa gnas mi mjed 'jig rten du ston pa
NK035(ci)004:1275: phrag gnyis bstan pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK035(ci)004:1276: las kyi rgyud lnga tshul lam thabs 'byung ba tsha
NK035(ci)004:1277: grang gi rang sgra las khyab 'jug zur phud lnga
NK035(ci)004:1278: pa'i skad kyis gsungs dus tshe lo bye ba gcig
NK035(ci)004:1279: thub pa'i dus na'o yang gsum pa gnas drod gsher
NK035(ci)004:1280: 'dus pa 'od kyi phung por ston pa 'jam dpal
NK035(ci)004:1281: 'jigs pa skyob pa 'khor byang chub sems dpa' 'bum
NK035(ci)004:1282: phrag drug bstan pa 'khor ba dong sprug dang rma
NK035(ci)004:1283: bya mjing bsnol dang dpal 'byung bzhi zad pa'i rgyud
NK035(ci)004:1284: bar snang gi khams su babs nas rlung gi sgra
NK035(ci)004:1285: mar sha shu las drangs te mkha' lding zur phud
NK035(ci)004:1286: gsum pa'i skad la bsgyur te gsungs so dus tshe
NK035(ci)004:1287: lo 'bum pa'i dus na'o yang bzhi pa gnas 'dod
NK035(ci)004:1288: chags 'byung ba mngal du snang bar ston pa gzhon
NK035(ci)004:1289: nu rol pa rnam par rtse ba 'khor gnod sbyin
NK035(ci)004:1290: dang brag srin stong phrag lnga la bstan pa sems
NK035(ci)004:1291: sde'i rgyud lnga dang yan lag gi rgyud drug ste
NK035(ci)004:1292: bcu gcig gsung dus tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus na'o
NK035(ci)004:1293: yang lnga pa gnas sman 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i ldum
NK035(ci)004:1294: rar ston pa drug pa rdo rje 'chang gis 'khor
NK035(ci)004:1295: sangs rgyas rabs bdun la bstan pa pha rol tu
NK035(ci)004:1296: phyin pa drug la sogs pa dpag tu med pa
NK035(ci)004:1297: gsungs dus tshe lo bdun khri'i dus na'o yang drug
NK035(ci)004:1298: pa gnas gsang chen rol pa'i dur khrod me ri
NK035(ci)004:1299: 'bar bar ston pa gzhon nu dpa' bo stobs ldan
NK035(ci)004:1300: chen pos 'khor byang chub sems dpa'i sprin gyi shugs
NK035(ci)004:1301: can bdun pa chos pha'i rgyud dang ma'i rgyud la
NK035(ci)004:1302: sogs pa'i rgyud sde du ma gsungs so dus tshe
NK035(ci)004:1303: lo drug khri'i dus na'o yang bdun pa gnas srin
NK035(ci)004:1304: po ru lu'i sgra dang ldan par ston pa drang
NK035(ci)004:1305: srong khros pa'i rgyal pos 'khor srin po bye ba
NK035(ci)004:1306: gcig la chos rags pa 'dul ba'i rgyud bcu la
NK035(ci)004:1307: sogs pa bstan te dus tshe lo khri pa'i dus
NK035(ci)004:1308: na'o yang brgyad pa gnas bya rgod phung po'i rgyal
NK035(ci)004:1309: po'i khab tu ston pa dgra bcom pa gser 'od
NK035(ci)004:1310: dam pas 'khor 'phags pa nyan thos rdzu 'phrul dang
NK035(ci)004:1311: ldan pa dpag tu med pa la chos dam pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1312: chos 'dul ba khri phrag dpag tu med par gsungs
NK035(ci)004:1313: so dus tshe lo lnga stong pa'i dus na'o yang
NK035(ci)004:1314: dgu pa gnas sog po g.yu'i smin ma can byang
NK035(ci)004:1315: chub kyi shing rnam par rgyal ba'i khang par ston
NK035(ci)004:1316: pa rtse bas rol pa'i blo gros kyis 'khor sa
NK035(ci)004:1317: brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la chos 'phra
NK035(ci)004:1318: rgyud bdun la sogs pa gsungs so dus tshe lo
NK035(ci)004:1319: stong pa'i dus na'o yang bcu pa gnas slar bya
NK035(ci)004:1320: rgod spungs par ston pa 'od srungs bsgres pos 'khor
NK035(ci)004:1321: tshe dang ldan pa dgra bcom pa bdun la dam
NK035(ci)004:1322: pa'i chos mdo sde dang sngags kri ya dang lung
NK035(ci)004:1323: a nu yo ga'i chos khri phrag phyed dang brgyad
NK035(ci)004:1324: la sogs pa gsungs so dus tshe lo lnga brgya'i
NK035(ci)004:1325: dus na'o yang bcu gcig pa gnas gdan byang chub
NK035(ci)004:1326: 'byung bar ston pa yab mngon rdzogs rgyal pos 'khor
NK035(ci)004:1327: rigs gsum mgon po la chos nges pa'i don 'ba'
NK035(ci)004:1328: zhig tu gsungs so dus tshe lo sum brgya pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1329: dus na'o yang bcu gnyis pa gnas phun sum tshogs
NK035(ci)004:1330: pa mgon med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra bar
NK035(ci)004:1331: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa sh+aakya thub pas 'khor
NK035(ci)004:1332: rnam pa bzhi la chos phun sum tshogs pa bden
NK035(ci)004:1333: pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo lan bcu gnyis su
NK035(ci)004:1334: bskor te de yang mi rtag pa dang sdug bsngal
NK035(ci)004:1335: ba dang stong pa dang bdag med pa dang kun
NK035(ci)004:1336: 'byung dang rgyu rkyen gyi rnam pa lam rig pa
NK035(ci)004:1337: 'gog pa zhi ba gya nom pa ste bcu gnyis
NK035(ci)004:1338: su bskor ro dus tshe lo brgya pa'i dus na'o
NK035(ci)004:1339: de ltar gnas bcu gnyis su byon pas na phun
NK035(ci)004:1340: sum tshogs pa cha lngar bstan pas bgrangs na chos
NK035(ci)004:1341: kyi rnam grangs drug cu tham par yod pa ni
NK035(ci)004:1342: bskal pa'i yar 'phel mar 'grib drug cu dag par
NK035(ci)004:1343: bya la dgongs pa'o de yang bstan pa'i gtso bo'am
NK035(ci)004:1344: bstan pa nges par sprul pa'i sku gcig la chos
NK035(ci)004:1345: kyi rnam pa dgu bcu rtsa drug tshogs dgos so
NK035(ci)004:1346: de dag dang ldan pa ni bdag ces bya'o gal
NK035(ci)004:1347: te mi ldan pa'i sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byung
NK035(ci)004:1348: na khol bu'i bstan pa zhes bya'o de dag kyang
NK035(ci)004:1349: sngon du sems bskyed rdzogs par byas pa las byung
NK035(ci)004:1350: ba'o mdzad pa'i 'phrin las kyi sgo nas sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)004:1351: pa ni sku'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis ni gnas mi
NK035(ci)004:1352: 'dra ba bcu gnyis su ston pa nyid kyi sku
NK035(ci)004:1353: mdog dang phyag mtshan mi 'dra bar sprul nas byon
NK035(ci)004:1354: te gdul bya'i rigs mi 'dra ba bcu gnyis kyi
NK035(ci)004:1355: tshogs rnams kyi don mdzad pas na mdzad pa zhes
NK035(ci)004:1356: sku'i gzi mdangs la brten nas nyid kyi sku'i bstan
NK035(ci)004:1357: pa 'phel ba'i don du byung ba'o yang sku de
NK035(ci)004:1358: dag gi dus su gsung chos kyi 'khor lo mi
NK035(ci)004:1359: 'dra ba bcu gnyis su gsungs pas 'gro ba'i ngag
NK035(ci)004:1360: gi bcings pa mi 'dra ba bcu gnyis grol bar
NK035(ci)004:1361: byed pas na mdzad pa zhes gsung gi bstan pa
NK035(ci)004:1362: 'phel bar byed pa'i don du byung ba'o gsung de
NK035(ci)004:1363: tsam zhig gi tshe na thugs kyi dgongs pa mi
NK035(ci)004:1364: 'dra ba bcu gnyis kyis 'gro ba'i rigs mi 'dra
NK035(ci)004:1365: ba rnams kyi sems kyi rtog pa bcu gnyis las
NK035(ci)004:1366: grol bar mdzad pas na mdzad pa zhes thugs kyi
NK035(ci)004:1367: bstan pa 'phel ba'i don du byung ba'o de ltar
NK035(ci)004:1368: byung bas 'gro ba'i lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig
NK035(ci)004:1369: pa dag byed du yang byung ba'o de yang sku'i
NK035(ci)004:1370: mdzad pa mdzad na sangs rgyas kyi sku gdul bya
NK035(ci)004:1371: la mi snang la gsung mdo sde yan lag tu
NK035(ci)004:1372: bstan pa la yid ches pa mi 'byung gsung gi
NK035(ci)004:1373: mdzad pa ma mdzad pa la sgom sgrub bzlas pa
NK035(ci)004:1374: 'i yon tan mthar mi phyin thugs kyi mdzad pa
NK035(ci)004:1375: mdzad na ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pas 'bras bu 'grub
NK035(ci)004:1376: par mi 'gyur ro de ltar mdzad pa dngos sku'i
NK035(ci)004:1377: mdzad pa bcu gnyis ni thun mong mi pham mgon
NK035(ci)004:1378: la rgyal sras dam par dbang bskur nas tha ma
NK035(ci)004:1379: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i tshul bstan pa
NK035(ci)004:1380: yan chad gzhan dang mthun gsung gi gnas bcu gnyis
NK035(ci)004:1381: su byung ba'o thugs ni dpa' bar 'gro ba la
NK035(ci)004:1382: sogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin bcu gnyis su byung ba'o
NK035(ci)004:1383: de'i phyir na ngo bo skur rgyas pa ni sku'i
NK035(ci)004:1384: mdzad par byung mkhyen pa'i ye shes su rgyas pa
NK035(ci)004:1385: ni gsung gi mdzad par byung gnas pa ting nge
NK035(ci)004:1386: 'dzin du rgyas pas thugs kyi mdzad par byung ngo
NK035(ci)004:1387: de yang bkod pa chen po las phyi la sogs
NK035(ci)004:1388: pa dgu yis ni mdzad pa'i bye brag dgongs par
NK035(ci)004:1389: 'gyur ro zhes pa nas mdzad pa'i dgongs pa ni
NK035(ci)004:1390: sku'i phyi nang gsang ba gsum gsung la phyi nang
NK035(ci)004:1391: gsang ba gsum thugs la phyi nang gsang ba gsum
NK035(ci)004:1392: ste dgur byas pas sku'i phyi'i mdzad pa bzhi ni
NK035(ci)004:1393: skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal mthong ba la brten
NK035(ci)004:1394: nas khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung zas
NK035(ci)004:1395: bsod snyoms gsol ba dang 'phong dang sgyu rtsal 'gran
NK035(ci)004:1396: pa rnams so nang gi 'khor dang longs spyod la
NK035(ci)004:1397: dgongs nas bdud bzhi pham par mdzad pa dang nyid
NK035(ci)004:1398: kyi sku las 'od zer bye ba khrag khrig brgya
NK035(ci)004:1399: stong drug cu byung ba dang bdud kyis mtshon cha'i
NK035(ci)004:1400: char phab pas me tog gi gdugs su gyur pa
NK035(ci)004:1401: dang rta mchog shing rta la sogs slar dor ba
NK035(ci)004:1402: rnams so gsang ba'i bzhi ni bya ba'i ting nge
NK035(ci)004:1403: 'dzin grol ba la dgongs nas chu bo nee rany+dza
NK035(ci)004:1404: na'i 'gram du dka' thub lo bdun mdzad pa dang
NK035(ci)004:1405: ri bo chen po gser ldan du ting nge 'dzin
NK035(ci)004:1406: 'bum phrag brgya nyi shu skad cig la skyes pa
NK035(ci)004:1407: dang khyad par du rin po che za ma tog
NK035(ci)004:1408: ces bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la dus thams cad
NK035(ci)004:1409: du snyoms par bzhugs pa dang sku mngon par mi
NK035(ci)004:1410: snang ba'i dus na nam phyed na rdo rje lta
NK035(ci)004:1411: bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par bzhugs so de
NK035(ci)004:1412: dag ni sangs rgyas kyi sku'i yon tan no gsung
NK035(ci)004:1413: gi phyi'i mdzad pa bzhi ni lung du bstan pa
NK035(ci)004:1414: la sogs pa bzhi nang gi bzhi ni skyes rabs
NK035(ci)004:1415: kyis la sogs pa bzhi gsang ba'i bzhi ni ched
NK035(ci)004:1416: du brjod pa la sogs pa bzhi'o de dag ni
NK035(ci)004:1417: gsung gi khyad par gyi 'dus pa'i khyad par las
NK035(ci)004:1418: byung ba'o thugs kyi phyi'i bzhi ni dpa' bar 'gro
NK035(ci)004:1419: ba'i dang rin po che rgyal mtshan tog gi dang
NK035(ci)004:1420: rnam par rol pa'i snyoms par zhugs pa dang sangs
NK035(ci)004:1421: rgyas za ma tog gi ting nge 'dzin to nang
NK035(ci)004:1422: gi bzhi ni yul kun la 'jug pa'i dang khyad
NK035(ci)004:1423: par mngon par snang ba'i dang gtsug gi nor bu'i
NK035(ci)004:1424: dang rgyal mtshan rtse mo yongs su bkod pa'i ting
NK035(ci)004:1425: nge 'dzin to gsang ba'i bzhi ni 'gyu ba rnam
NK035(ci)004:1426: par dag pa'i dang zab mo snang ba'i dang rin
NK035(ci)004:1427: po che sgron ma'i dang mchog tu legs pa brjod
NK035(ci)004:1428: pa'i ting nge 'dzin to de dag gi dgos pa
NK035(ci)004:1429: ni sku'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis med na sku mtshan
NK035(ci)004:1430: bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad bzang
NK035(ci)004:1431: po brgyad cur mi smin la gsung gi med na
NK035(ci)004:1432: mtshan ma med pa'i chos la longs spyod mi nus
NK035(ci)004:1433: thugs kyi med na ting nge 'dzin rnams la dbang
NK035(ci)004:1434: mi thob bo de yang gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK035(ci)004:1435: med na nam yang mkhyen pa'i ye shes su rgyas
NK035(ci)004:1436: mi srid do de ltar bcu gnyis su nges pa
NK035(ci)004:1437: ni phyi'i sku'i dgos pa ni 'byung ba sas bcings
NK035(ci)004:1438: nus pa rang rgyud du 'dzin pa las mi grol
NK035(ci)004:1439: bas na'o de bzhin du chus dang mes dang rlung
NK035(ci)004:1440: gis bcings pa dbugs rang rgyud du 'dzin pa las
NK035(ci)004:1441: mi grol bas na'o nang gi bzhi ni 'byung ba
NK035(ci)004:1442: sa'i bstan pa 'jig pa dang sa'i byer ba khungs
NK035(ci)004:1443: su 'jug pa dang sa'i snyoms pas 'gro ba bskyed
NK035(ci)004:1444: pa'o de bzhin du lhag ma gsum yang shes so
NK035(ci)004:1445: gsang ba'i bzhi ni lus kyi rdos pa zad pa
NK035(ci)004:1446: dang ngag gi brjod pa dag pa dang yid kyi
NK035(ci)004:1447: 'gyu ba dag pa dang sems kyi rtog pa dag
NK035(ci)004:1448: pa'o gsung gi phyi'i bzhi ni phung po'i bdud gzugs
NK035(ci)004:1449: can ma yin pas dag pa dang nyon mongs pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1450: bdud 'dod pa dang ngar 'dzin med pas dag pa
NK035(ci)004:1451: dang lha'i bu'i bdud zhen chags med pas dag pa
NK035(ci)004:1452: dang 'chi bdag gi bdud chos nyid skye ba med
NK035(ci)004:1453: pas dag pa'o nang gi bzhi ni lus ngag yid
NK035(ci)004:1454: ma bcos pas 'dul ba rnam par dag pa brjod
NK035(ci)004:1455: med pas mdo sde rnam par dag pa sems rang
NK035(ci)004:1456: sa na gsal bas mngon par dag pa phyogs kun
NK035(ci)004:1457: tu shar bas rigs 'dzin gyi sde snod rnam par
NK035(ci)004:1458: dag pa'o gsang ba'i bzhi ni mur thug pa rnam
NK035(ci)004:1459: par dag pas 'jig rten las grol mu stegs rnam
NK035(ci)004:1460: par dag pas bdag med kyi don la gnas phyal
NK035(ci)004:1461: ba rnam par dag pas 'bras bu mngon par 'byin
NK035(ci)004:1462: rgyang 'phen pa rnam par dag pas las rgyu 'bras
NK035(ci)004:1463: la yid ches gsang ba'i ni lta ba log pa
NK035(ci)004:1464: dag pas sku gsum tshad du phyin sgom pa log
NK035(ci)004:1465: pa dag pas mnyam rjes zung du 'brel spyod pa
NK035(ci)004:1466: log pa dag pas lam yang dag pa dang ldan
NK035(ci)004:1467: 'bras bu log pa dag pas sku gsum lam du
NK035(ci)004:1468: snang ba'o thugs kyi phyi'i bzhi ni gzhi la phyin
NK035(ci)004:1469: ci log tu 'dzin pa'i gcer bu ba rnam par
NK035(ci)004:1470: dag pas gzhi nas ye grol lam la phyin ci
NK035(ci)004:1471: log tu lta ba'i rgyang 'phen pa rnam par dag
NK035(ci)004:1472: pas ma bcos rang grol snang ba la phyin ci
NK035(ci)004:1473: log tu lta ba'i ser skya ba rnam par dag
NK035(ci)004:1474: pas gcer bzhag gcer grol 'bras bu la phyin ci
NK035(ci)004:1475: log tu lta ba'i rigs byed gsang ba dag pas
NK035(ci)004:1476: rang snang yongs grol lo nang gi ni zas la
NK035(ci)004:1477: zhen pa chod pas kham gyi zas bdag tu med
NK035(ci)004:1478: gos kyi zhen pa chod pas gcer bu bsam gtan
NK035(ci)004:1479: gyi thun la spyod rmi lam gyi zhen pa chod
NK035(ci)004:1480: pas bag chags kyi mtha' stongs pa'i thun la spyod
NK035(ci)004:1481: bag chags kyi zhen pa chod pas las dang rnam
NK035(ci)004:1482: par smin pa'i mtha' stongs so gsang ba'i ni snang
NK035(ci)004:1483: ba rang snang rang grol du shes pas sprul pa
NK035(ci)004:1484: sku'i 'bras bu thob 'gyu ba rang snang rang grol
NK035(ci)004:1485: bas longs sku'i mkhyen pa ye shes rdzogs gnas pa
NK035(ci)004:1486: rang thog tu grol bas chos sku'i mkhyen pa ma
NK035(ci)004:1487: lus par rdzogs snang stong gnyis med du grol bas
NK035(ci)004:1488: ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i mkhyen pa yongs su rdzogs
NK035(ci)004:1489: pa ste des na phyi rol pa dang nang pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1490: ston pa'i khyad par ro de ltar dus gsum sangs
NK035(ci)004:1491: rgyas dgongs pas brgyud pa ni byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK035(ci)004:1492: brgyud pa zhes bya ste 'das pa dang ma 'os
NK035(ci)004:1493: pa dang da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad
NK035(ci)004:1494: kyi rang bzhin rnam dag gi byin brlabs so de
NK035(ci)004:1495: yang brjod bya'i tshig la ma brten par chos nyid
NK035(ci)004:1496: kyi rang sgra la brten nas rtogs shing khong du
NK035(ci)004:1497: chud pa'o de yang dus ni mi 'gyur ba la
NK035(ci)004:1498: bya gsum ni grangs sangs pa ni las dang nyon
NK035(ci)004:1499: mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa med pa la
NK035(ci)004:1500: rgyas pa ni ngo bo skur rgyas pas sku gsum
NK035(ci)004:1501: 'du 'bral med mkhyen pa ye shes gsum las mi
NK035(ci)004:1502: 'da' gnas pa ting nge 'dzin du rgyas pas dus
NK035(ci)004:1503: thams cad rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin las
NK035(ci)004:1504: mi phyed mdzad pa phrin las su rgyas pas mdzad
NK035(ci)004:1505: pa sum cu rtsa drug mthar phyung dgongs pa ni
NK035(ci)004:1506: chos kyi sku la dgongs pa dmigs pa mi mnga'
NK035(ci)004:1507: bas ye nas ye grol du gnas longs sku la
NK035(ci)004:1508: gsal la rtog pa med pas rang snang rang grol
NK035(ci)004:1509: la gnas sprul pa'i sku la zhen chags dang bral
NK035(ci)004:1510: bas gcig skye gcig 'gag la gnas pa'o brgyud pa
NK035(ci)004:1511: ni lhag pa dang chad pa med pa'i don te
NK035(ci)004:1512: bskal pa thog ma med pa nas da lta'i rnal
NK035(ci)004:1513: 'byor pa yan chad la tshig la lhag chad med
NK035(ci)004:1514: cing don la 'khrul pa med pa ste dper na
NK035(ci)004:1515: rin po che'i snod la rgyas btab pa lta bu
NK035(ci)004:1516: dang rgyal po'i bka' rtags lta bu'o lo du ma
NK035(ci)004:1517: lon kyang rgyus da lta'i mi ltar yod pa la
NK035(ci)004:1518: lo rgyus zhes bya'o de'i phyin na lo rgyud don
NK035(ci)004:1519: gyis ma bshad na gsang chen rgyal ba'i bka' 'di
NK035(ci)004:1520: la yid mi ches pa'i skyon du 'gyur zhes pa'o
NK035(ci)004:1521: bla ma gong ma'i gsung bgros las lhag pa dang
NK035(ci)004:1522: chad pa med par bum pa tshad ldan nas tshad
NK035(ci)004:1523: ldan du bkang ba lta bur song ba mi brgyud
NK035(ci)004:1524: pa zhes bya'o de yang 'di dag rnams shes shing
NK035(ci)004:1525: khong du chud pa rnams la sangs rgyas kyi byin
NK035(ci)004:1526: brlabs nges par 'byung bar 'gyur ro de na brgyud
NK035(ci)004:1527: pa'i man ngag gtso ba'o de dag ni rgyal ba
NK035(ci)004:1528: dgongs pa'i brgyud pa'o i thi lo rgyu chen mo'i
NK035(ci)004:1529: smad cha gnas 'byed bdun pa bzhugs so rgya gar
NK035(ci)004:1530: skad du b+ha du ba tri sa ka ri n+aa
NK035(ci)004:1531: ma bod skad du gnas 'byed bdun pa zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:1532: ba lo rgyus chen mo gtan la dbab pa'o rdo
NK035(ci)004:1533: rje 'chang chen 'gro ba yongs kyi bla bla ma
NK035(ci)004:1534: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa 'chang ba dang ye
NK035(ci)004:1535: shes las la grub pa'i mkha' 'gro ma skyabs mdzad
NK035(ci)004:1536: mchod 'os rnams la phyag 'tshal lo gang zhig lo
NK035(ci)004:1537: rgyus don nyid tshad ma blor bzhag nas ma 'ongs
NK035(ci)004:1538: dus kyi gang zag the tshom can nges shes 'jug
NK035(ci)004:1539: par bya phyir mig gi rgyan sogs spro bla ma
NK035(ci)004:1540: grub thob phung po mi snang bar zag pa rang
NK035(ci)004:1541: zad dbyings su sku gshegs pa'i rig 'dzin gong ma
NK035(ci)004:1542: rnams kyi lo rgyus nyid gsang ba sgra yi rgyud
NK035(ci)004:1543: dang bkod pa chen po las ji ltar gsungs pa
NK035(ci)004:1544: nyid las lhag dang chad pa med ma nor nges
NK035(ci)004:1545: pa tshig sdebs yi ge yang 'di la 'jug 'dod
NK035(ci)004:1546: skal ldan snying gi bu mngon sum gnad la 'bebs
NK035(ci)004:1547: pa'i don ched du lo rgyus don nyid tshig gis
NK035(ci)004:1548: rgyas bshad do de la rigs ni rdo rje 'chang
NK035(ci)004:1549: chen po khyad par gyi yon tan dgu bcu rtsa
NK035(ci)004:1550: drug dang ldan pa 'adi'o 'dzin pa ni gnad la
NK035(ci)004:1551: brten nas nyams blangs pas de nyid ci 'dra bar
NK035(ci)004:1552: byed pa'o de yang sus 'dzin na slob dpon chen
NK035(ci)004:1553: po dga' rab rdo rje la sogs pa sprul pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1554: sku de dag rnams la bya'o brda' ni ngo bo
NK035(ci)004:1555: dang nges tshig dang dbye ba'o ngo bo ni gnad
NK035(ci)004:1556: thog tu phebs par byed pa'o gnad thog ni me
NK035(ci)004:1557: btsa' lta bu'o nges tshig ni tshig tsam mo sgra
NK035(ci)004:1558: tsam gyi na brda' tsam la brten nas chos nyid
NK035(ci)004:1559: gtan la 'bebs par byed pas na brda zhes bya'o
NK035(ci)004:1560: dbye na brda'i gnad gzhan dpag tu med pa cig
NK035(ci)004:1561: yod kyang rang bzhin gyi brda dang bya shing bstan
NK035(ci)004:1562: pa'i brda dang brjod pa'i brda las mi 'ada'o rang
NK035(ci)004:1563: bzhin gnas pa dang rtags su bkod pa gnyis so
NK035(ci)004:1564: gnas pa ni phyi yul gyi snang ba la brten
NK035(ci)004:1565: nas brda don gyi man ngag tu 'gyur bas phyi
NK035(ci)004:1566: yi snang ba ma spangs par sangs rgya ba dang
NK035(ci)004:1567: nang sems kyi rtog pa ma lus par brda don
NK035(ci)004:1568: gyi man ngag tu 'gyur ba'o rtags su bkod pa
NK035(ci)004:1569: ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku'i rten dang gsung dang
NK035(ci)004:1570: thugs kyi rten la sogs pa'o de dag la brten
NK035(ci)004:1571: nas brda don gyi man ngag la brten nas sangs
NK035(ci)004:1572: rgya'o byas shing brten pa'i brda la gnyis te lus
NK035(ci)004:1573: kyi brda dang yid kyi barda'o lus la gsum ste
NK035(ci)004:1574: lag gi 'du byed kyi brda dang bris pa yi
NK035(ci)004:1575: ge'i brda dang byas pa gzugs brnyan gyi barda'o lag
NK035(ci)004:1576: gi 'du byed ni rang gi sde pas go la
NK035(ci)004:1577: gzhan gyis mi go bas dngos grub kyi rgyur 'gro
NK035(ci)004:1578: ba ni sngags kyi rgyud so so'i skabs na ji
NK035(ci)004:1579: ltar byas pa'i rim pa rnams bshad pa de rnams
NK035(ci)004:1580: so bris pa yi ge'i brda ni 'gyu byed kyi
NK035(ci)004:1581: yi ge la brten nas snang srid rang grol du
NK035(ci)004:1582: grol ba'i gnad dang dag byed kyi yi ge la
NK035(ci)004:1583: brten nas srid gsum rang dag la grol ba'i gnad
NK035(ci)004:1584: do sgyur byed yi ge la brten nas gsang ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1585: don kun mngon du bstan pa yang kun gyis mi
NK035(ci)004:1586: go bar bstan pa ni lha'i yi ge dang mkha'
NK035(ci)004:1587: 'gro ma smra byed kyi yi ge dang klu'i yi
NK035(ci)004:1588: ge dang tshangs pa dang nam mkha' lding gi yi
NK035(ci)004:1589: ge la sogs pa rnams la sbyangs pas bdag nyid
NK035(ci)004:1590: kyis shes shing go bas gzhan gyis mi go ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1591: gnad do spros pa yi ge'i sbrel ba la brten
NK035(ci)004:1592: nas gsang sngags kyi bzlas pa'i gnad la mkhas par
NK035(ci)004:1593: 'gyur ba'o byas pa gzugs brnyan gyi brda ni kham
NK035(ci)004:1594: sa'i mi mo dang mar me'i kong bu la sogs
NK035(ci)004:1595: pa byas pa'i rnam pa la brten nas khyad par
NK035(ci)004:1596: du nges shes skyes par byed pa'o yid kyi brda
NK035(ci)004:1597: ni byin gyis brlabs tshogs dang gtor ma la brten
NK035(ci)004:1598: nas bla ma'i dgongs pa tshad dang ldan par gyur
NK035(ci)004:1599: pa dang yid kyi dad pas rig pa gnyis med
NK035(ci)004:1600: du grol ba dang yid sems 'dres par byed pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1601: gnad do 'di dag ni bla ma'i dgongs pa'i gnad
NK035(ci)004:1602: las byung ba'o mi snang ba la sogs pa yid
NK035(ci)004:1603: kyi brda zhes pa'i don do brjod pa'i brda la
NK035(ci)004:1604: gsum ste lung las byung ba'i brda rnal 'byor shes
NK035(ci)004:1605: pas nyams las byung ba'i brda dus nges pa la
NK035(ci)004:1606: ched du brjod pa'i barda'o lung las byung ba ni
NK035(ci)004:1607: rang gi dam tshig nye bar mtshon pa gsang sngags
NK035(ci)004:1608: rgyud so so las byung ba rnams te 'gro ba
NK035(ci)004:1609: gzhan gyi mi go ba dper na kla klo'i skad
NK035(ci)004:1610: lta bu'o rnal 'byor shes pa'i nyams las byung ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1611: brda 'gro ba gzhan gyi sdug bsngal las grol bar
NK035(ci)004:1612: byed pa rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba dang sems
NK035(ci)004:1613: chos dang 'dres par byed pa la sogs pa nyams
NK035(ci)004:1614: dang sbyar zhing spyod pa nyid grub pa thob pa
NK035(ci)004:1615: rnams kyi spyod yul lo dus nges pa la ched
NK035(ci)004:1616: du brjod pa ni tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus dang
NK035(ci)004:1617: dbang bskur ba'i dus sam dpa' bo dpa' mo'i ston
NK035(ci)004:1618: mo byed pa'i dus su brjod pa ste de dag
NK035(ci)004:1619: la brten nas phyi'i spros pa gcod pa dang nang
NK035(ci)004:1620: du chos nyid kyi don mngon sum du skye'o brda
NK035(ci)004:1621: de dag la brten nas nyams su myong ba thod
NK035(ci)004:1622: rgal du skye bar byed pa'i gnad yin no de
NK035(ci)004:1623: ltar brda'i rang bzhin khong du chud par byed do
NK035(ci)004:1624: de nyid chud pas tshig dang yi ge'i spros pa
NK035(ci)004:1625: gcod pa'o de lta bu'i don de su la brgyud
NK035(ci)004:1626: na sprul pa po dga' rab rdo rje la brgyud
NK035(ci)004:1627: sus brgyud na dpal rdo rje 'chang gis brgyud brgyud
NK035(ci)004:1628: tshul lam thabs ji ltar brgyud na gsang sngags thams
NK035(ci)004:1629: cad brda du ma la brten nas brgyud de dpe
NK035(ci)004:1630: ji ltar brgyud na bum pa tshad ldan nas tshad
NK035(ci)004:1631: ldan du bkang ba ltar lhag pa med cing ma
NK035(ci)004:1632: gang ba med par ltar brgyud do ci'i phyir brgyud
NK035(ci)004:1633: na ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi skal ldan rnams la
NK035(ci)004:1634: nges pa'i don cig car du bskyed pa'i phyir brgyud
NK035(ci)004:1635: de ltar brgyud pa dgos pa ci yod na 'bras
NK035(ci)004:1636: bu sangs rgyas pa'i dgos pa ma 'khrul pa dang
NK035(ci)004:1637: rnam par rtog pa mtha' dag pa'i blos sgros gdags
NK035(ci)004:1638: su med pa'o de la sangs rgyas mya ngan las
NK035(ci)004:1639: 'das nas lo sum brgya dang drug cu tham pa
NK035(ci)004:1640: na rgya gar rdo rje gdan gyi nub phyogs o
NK035(ci)004:1641: rgyan thor cog can gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i
NK035(ci)004:1642: gling zhes bya ba na tsan+dana gyi shing ljon pa
NK035(ci)004:1643: rnams kyis bskor ba ko sha na zhes bya ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1644: srog chags lus mi la gdong dred sder mo rnams
NK035(ci)004:1645: lcags kyi sbar shad kyis gtams pa rgyu rnams rin
NK035(ci)004:1646: po che phra mos gtams pa dpag tu med pas
NK035(ci)004:1647: gang ba d+ha na ko sha'i gling zhes bya'o d+ha
NK035(ci)004:1648: ni tsan+dana gyi gling rnams la bya'o de nas bkra
NK035(ci)004:1649: shis bde byed brtsegs pa zhes bya ba'i gtsug lag
NK035(ci)004:1650: khang chen po zhig na gtsug lag khang phra mo
NK035(ci)004:1651: stong drug brgya dang brgyad kyis phyogs mtshams rnams yongs
NK035(ci)004:1652: su bskor ba de dag gi bar gser gyi dril
NK035(ci)004:1653: bu g.yer kha'i d+r+wa ba'i thag pas rab tu sbrel
NK035(ci)004:1654: ba shin tu mdzes shing nyams dga' ba dang ldan
NK035(ci)004:1655: pa na mi rnams kyang gzugs bzang zhing yan lag
NK035(ci)004:1656: rags pa la spyi bor ral pa'i thor tshugs bcings
NK035(ci)004:1657: pa gser dang dngul dang mu men la sogs pas
NK035(ci)004:1658: brgyan pa ras dkar dmar sna tshogs gon pa sha
NK035(ci)004:1659: stag go bud med rnams skra'i mdud pa mdun rgyab
NK035(ci)004:1660: gnyis su 'ching ba'o de dag la dung dang rus
NK035(ci)004:1661: pa'i rgyan sna tshogs pas brgyan pa'o yul de na
NK035(ci)004:1662: yab rgyal po u pa r+aa dza zhes bya ba
NK035(ci)004:1663: la yum snang ba gsal ba'i 'od ldan ma zhes
NK035(ci)004:1664: bya ba zhig yod de de gnyis la sras mo
NK035(ci)004:1665: su d+ha ra ma zhes bya ba rab tu byung
NK035(ci)004:1666: nas yun ring po ma lon pa bsnyen par rdzogs
NK035(ci)004:1667: nas yun ring po ma lon pa'i dge slong ma
NK035(ci)004:1668: gcig de nas dpag tshad gcig 'das pa'i nub na
NK035(ci)004:1669: gser gyi bye ma brdal ba'i rgya mtsho'i gling na
NK035(ci)004:1670: 'jag ma'i spyil po phub nas g.yog mo bde ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1671: snying rje ldan zhes bya ba mkha' 'gro ma gcig
NK035(ci)004:1672: gis byed cing dge sbyor skyong gin bzhugs pa'i lha
NK035(ci)004:1673: lcam gyi mtshan mo rmi lam na mi dkar po
NK035(ci)004:1674: rin po che shel las grub pa ring ba mdung
NK035(ci)004:1675: tsam pa gcig gis spyi bor gtsug tu rin po
NK035(ci)004:1676: che shel gyi bum pa la yi ge +amo +aahmh'u
NK035(ci)004:1677: s+w+aa h+aa zhes rigs lnga'i dbang bskur ba'i rtags su
NK035(ci)004:1678: de dag gis rgyas btab pa gcig spyi bo'i steng
NK035(ci)004:1679: du lan gsum bzhag pas bum pa de las 'od
NK035(ci)004:1680: 'phros pas khams gsum dus cig gsal bar mthong ba
NK035(ci)004:1681: zhig rmis de nas nang par rmi lam de la
NK035(ci)004:1682: ngo mtshar che nas tsha ba'i dus su g.yog mo
NK035(ci)004:1683: la bshad pas g.yog mo des na re lha lcam
NK035(ci)004:1684: nyid la sprul pa'i sku gcig 'khrungs pa'i ltas yin
NK035(ci)004:1685: zer ro g.yog mo de ni mkha' 'gro ma pur
NK035(ci)004:1686: rna nye bar zhi ba zhes bya ba yin no
NK035(ci)004:1687: lha lcam gyi bsam pa la de ci la zer
NK035(ci)004:1688: snyam pa cig byung ngo de nas lha lcam de
NK035(ci)004:1689: lus ma bde nas rab tu sdug bsngal dang ldan
NK035(ci)004:1690: par gyur to de nas zla ba dgu ngo bcu
NK035(ci)004:1691: lon pa na lha lcam de la pha med pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1692: bu gcig rtsibs log g.yas pa'i go bar nas 'khrungs
NK035(ci)004:1693: so de 'khrungs pa dang dge slong ma de nyid
NK035(ci)004:1694: rab tu bred do kha nas pha med bu 'di
NK035(ci)004:1695: 'jig rten 'dre las min pa su 'jig rten bdud
NK035(ci)004:1696: dam tshangs pa la sogs sam rgyal po btsan dang
NK035(ci)004:1697: dmu la sogs pa'i rigs khams gsum dag na 'dod
NK035(ci)004:1698: ldan su zhig yin gal te lha 'am lha min
NK035(ci)004:1699: sna tshogs gzugs 'di ltar byung ba'i dpe ni su
NK035(ci)004:1700: yang mthong ba med rgyal khams chos med 'di ni
NK035(ci)004:1701: su la srid kye ma bdag ni rab tu khrims
NK035(ci)004:1702: gtsang 'gro las rgyal 'dod pas 'di ni log sred
NK035(ci)004:1703: 'gro bas dpyas gyur sdig re che zhes tshigs bcad
NK035(ci)004:1704: mang po brjod cing rab tu sdug bsngal bas g.yog
NK035(ci)004:1705: mo des ni 'di sangs rgyas kyi sras gcig yin
NK035(ci)004:1706: byas kyang ma nyan nas 'di thal ba'i dong du
NK035(ci)004:1707: sbos te bsrubs la zhog ces thal ba'i dong du
NK035(ci)004:1708: bor nas 'od dang sgra la sogs pa byung ngo
NK035(ci)004:1709: de nas zhag gsum lon nas bltas pas skad lhag
NK035(ci)004:1710: lhag byas nas ci yang ma nyes bar 'dug nas
NK035(ci)004:1711: slar dar dkar po dri ma med pa zhig gis
NK035(ci)004:1712: sle la blangs te spos chu dang 'o ma la
NK035(ci)004:1713: sogs pa'i khrus chab nas bton te 'di mi 'chi
NK035(ci)004:1714: ba'i lugs sam sprul par 'dug snyam nas blangs pas
NK035(ci)004:1715: bar snang nas lha rnams kyis bkra shis kyi tshigs
NK035(ci)004:1716: su bcad pa mgon po ston pa bcom ldan 'das
NK035(ci)004:1717: rang bzhin snang mdzad 'jig rten mgon bdag kyang rab
NK035(ci)004:1718: tu bskyab pa dang nam mkha'i rdo rje bdag la
NK035(ci)004:1719: gsol zhes brjod do mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis mchod
NK035(ci)004:1720: pa'i sprin gtibs pa dang lha dang klu dang gnod
NK035(ci)004:1721: sbyin la sogs pas tsan+dana gur gum gyi char phab
NK035(ci)004:1722: pa dang phyogs kun nas 'jig rten gyi khams skyong
NK035(ci)004:1723: ba rnams kyi chos kyi rnga chen po brdung ba
NK035(ci)004:1724: dang dung 'bud pa dang rgyal mtshan 'jugs pa dang
NK035(ci)004:1725: ba dan slong ba sogs pa dang drang srong gi
NK035(ci)004:1726: rgyal po chen po rnams kyis kyang sman gyi tshogs
NK035(ci)004:1727: dpag tu med pa'i sprin gyis gtibs so de nas
NK035(ci)004:1728: byis pa de gsol bas gzhan gyi zhag gsos pa
NK035(ci)004:1729: bas de'i za ma gsol pa skyed che ba gcig
NK035(ci)004:1730: byung ngo gzhan gyi lo dang de'i zla ba gnyis
NK035(ci)004:1731: de'i zla ba skyed che ba gcig byung ngo de
NK035(ci)004:1732: nas lo bdun lon tsa na khye'u de'i zhal nas
NK035(ci)004:1733: yum la kye ma gcig lags pan+di ta mkhas pa
NK035(ci)004:1734: rnams la zhe sa na ma gcig tsam yang 'bul
NK035(ci)004:1735: chos gtam ma bde ba 'ga' tsam yang zhu bas
NK035(ci)004:1736: yum gyis bdag la gnang bar zhu zhes zhu ba
NK035(ci)004:1737: phul bas yum de yi zhal nas bu kha nas
NK035(ci)004:1738: so'u ma barjesa par chos gtam ci la 'ong zer
NK035(ci)004:1739: bas khye'u de'i zhal nas ci nas kyang gnang bar
NK035(ci)004:1740: zhu zer te zhu ba drag tu phul bas yul
NK035(ci)004:1741: gyi zhal nas 'di nas shar gyi phyogs na dpag
NK035(ci)004:1742: tshad gcig 'das pa na d+ha na ko sha rab
NK035(ci)004:1743: tu snang ba'i gling zhes bya ba na bu rang
NK035(ci)004:1744: gi mes po rgyal po u pa r+aa dza zhes
NK035(ci)004:1745: bya ba mchod gnas pan+di ta lnga brgya yod pas
NK035(ci)004:1746: der song la zhus shig zer nas yum gyis gnang
NK035(ci)004:1747: ngo de nas khye'u rab tu dga' nas yul de
NK035(ci)004:1748: nyid du phyin te rgyal po dang mjal te rgyal
NK035(ci)004:1749: po la phyag byas nas bdag ni khyed kyi dbon
NK035(ci)004:1750: po lags te rgyal po chen po lags khyed pan+di
NK035(ci)004:1751: ta lnga brgya mchod gnas su bzhugs par gda' bas
NK035(ci)004:1752: bdag pan+di ta de rnams la zhe sa na ma
NK035(ci)004:1753: gcig tsam yang 'bul chos gtam zhig ma bde ba
NK035(ci)004:1754: 'ga' tsam yang zhu bas rgyal po chen po lags
NK035(ci)004:1755: bdag la gnang bar zhu ba phul bas rgyal po
NK035(ci)004:1756: des spyan gyis bltas te byis pa kha nas so'u
NK035(ci)004:1757: ma barjesa pa gcig gis chos gtam dang ci la
NK035(ci)004:1758: yong ste zhe sa yang ci la yong zer te
NK035(ci)004:1759: de nas khye'u de'i zhal nas rgyal po lags bdag
NK035(ci)004:1760: la ci nas kyang gnang bar zhu zhes glengs so
NK035(ci)004:1761: rgyal po'i zhal nas khyod lo ni byis par 'dug
NK035(ci)004:1762: ste sangs rgyas kyi mtshan rtags mang pos lus la
NK035(ci)004:1763: spras 'dug pas gal te sprul pa gcig yin srid
NK035(ci)004:1764: pas pan+di ta rnams dang mjal du gzhug gi gsungs
NK035(ci)004:1765: nas nang du gshegs so de nas pan+di ta rnams
NK035(ci)004:1766: gro gsol ba'i dus su rgyal pos gong gi khye'u
NK035(ci)004:1767: de'i gtam de dag pan+di ta rnams la bsnyad do
NK035(ci)004:1768: pan+di ta'i la la'i zer zhal nas smyon tshig dga'
NK035(ci)004:1769: dga' byed pa min nam nang du ma gtang gsungs
NK035(ci)004:1770: la la ci zer de dag gi nang nas mkhyen
NK035(ci)004:1771: pa che ba gcig gi zhal nas de yar thong
NK035(ci)004:1772: dang gal te sprul pa 'dra yong ba yang ma
NK035(ci)004:1773: nges mdangs sum gyi rmi lam na ltas bzang ba
NK035(ci)004:1774: gcig kyang byung gsungs nas nang du thong dang gsungs
NK035(ci)004:1775: nas nang du btang bas khye'u des phyag mdzad nas
NK035(ci)004:1776: de rnams la khye'u des rim pa bzhin kha nas
NK035(ci)004:1777: bgro gleng btang bas gang gis kyang ma thub tshur
NK035(ci)004:1778: chos gang dris kyang thogs pa dang rdugs pa med
NK035(ci)004:1779: par byung nas pan+di ta rnams kyis tshur la phyag
NK035(ci)004:1780: mdzad nas zhabs spyi gtsugs tu blangs nas rab tu
NK035(ci)004:1781: bstod de mtshan yang shes rab rgya che ba la
NK035(ci)004:1782: dgongs nas pra dz+ny+aa b+ha wa zhes bya bar btags
NK035(ci)004:1783: so rgyal po dgyes nas slob dpon dga' rab rdo
NK035(ci)004:1784: rje bya bar btags so yum gyis thal ba'i khung
NK035(ci)004:1785: bur sbas nas ma shi bas slob dpon chen po
NK035(ci)004:1786: ro langs thal mdog ces bya bar btags so yul
NK035(ci)004:1787: de'i mi kun gyi gzhon nu shin tu yid du
NK035(ci)004:1788: 'ong ba gcig rab tu bde bar 'dug nas slob
NK035(ci)004:1789: dpon ro langs bde ba ces bya bar thogs shig
NK035(ci)004:1790: ces grags so de ltar mtshan bzhir grags pa ni
NK035(ci)004:1791: skye ba bzhi'i sems can rnams kyi lus su nyid
NK035(ci)004:1792: kyis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyi gsung nyan cing
NK035(ci)004:1793: nye 'khor du 'khor bas de nyid kyi bsod nams
NK035(ci)004:1794: kyi stobs las grub pa'o de nas byang gi phyogs
NK035(ci)004:1795: na ri bo nyi ma rab tu snang bar byed
NK035(ci)004:1796: pa zhes bya bar brag rab tu 'jigs pa'i tshogs
NK035(ci)004:1797: la yi dwags drag po gnas pa'i steng du 'jag
NK035(ci)004:1798: ma'i spyil po phub ste lo sum cu rtsa gnyis
NK035(ci)004:1799: kyi bar la ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par bzhugs
NK035(ci)004:1800: pa'i tshul bstan pas sa g.yo ba lan bdun byung
NK035(ci)004:1801: nam mkha' las kyang sgra'i bye brag dpag tu med
NK035(ci)004:1802: pa byung me tog sna tshogs pa'i char yang babs
NK035(ci)004:1803: mu stegs kyi bstan pa yang nyams par byas so
NK035(ci)004:1804: zhes bya ba'i sgra yang skabs su byung bas yul
NK035(ci)004:1805: de'i mda' na mu stegs sdig skyong ba'i rgyal po
NK035(ci)004:1806: gcig yod pas de'i phyugs 'tsho ba'i byis pa rnams
NK035(ci)004:1807: kyis mthong ste rna ba la ra dung bus kyang
NK035(ci)004:1808: ma langs smyug ma'i u b+hi btsugs pas kyang ma
NK035(ci)004:1809: langs ci yang mi snyem pa gcig 'dug pa mthong
NK035(ci)004:1810: ste rgyal po la bsnyad pas rgyal po na re
NK035(ci)004:1811: 'di ni sangs rgyas kyis bstan pa 'phel ba mu
NK035(ci)004:1812: stegs kyi bstan pa nyams smad par byed pa yin
NK035(ci)004:1813: pas gshed ma gnyis kyis song la gsod cig ces
NK035(ci)004:1814: de gnyis la gri gu gnyis gtad nas btang ngo
NK035(ci)004:1815: gshed mas gsod par byas pas ci byas kyang glags
NK035(ci)004:1816: ma rnyed do slob dpon nam mkha' la sprin gyi
NK035(ci)004:1817: gseb nas lam phyungs te gshegs pas mu stegs rgyal
NK035(ci)004:1818: po 'khor dang bcas pa ngo mtshar skyes te phyag
NK035(ci)004:1819: byas nas rab tu bstod do sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK035(ci)004:1820: pa la zhugs so de ltar dgung lo sum cu
NK035(ci)004:1821: rtsa gnyis lon nas sngar gyi dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1822: sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs pa'i sde snod rin po
NK035(ci)004:1823: che ma lus pa dang khyad par du rang bzhin
NK035(ci)004:1824: rdzogs pa chen po sho lo ka 'bum phrag drug
NK035(ci)004:1825: cu rtsa bzhi thugs la gsungs pa rnams ri ma
NK035(ci)004:1826: la ya'i rin po che rnams spungs pa bstan pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1827: las rgyas pa'i rtse mo la rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK035(ci)004:1828: mkha' 'gro ma 'jig rten bde ba'i ro dang ldan
NK035(ci)004:1829: pa zhes bya ba gdong gsum pa stag gi phags
NK035(ci)004:1830: pa gyon pa phyag bzhi rma bya'i gdugs 'dzin pa
NK035(ci)004:1831: las su stag dang seng ge la zhon pa bde
NK035(ci)004:1832: byed ser mo yon tan mtha' yas pa'i mkha' 'gro
NK035(ci)004:1833: ma zhes bya ba 'brug la zhon cing glog gi
NK035(ci)004:1834: ga sha thogs pa rab tu khros pa yid bde
NK035(ci)004:1835: ba dang slob dpon nyid dang sangs rgyas kyis gsungs
NK035(ci)004:1836: pa lo gsum gyi bar du tshig dang yi ge
NK035(ci)004:1837: dkar chag la mnan rang byung rang babs kyi yi
NK035(ci)004:1838: ge sprul pa'i sku dang bcas pa phyin ci ma
NK035(ci)004:1839: log par legs par yi ge la bkod do de
NK035(ci)004:1840: ltar bkod nas mkha' 'gro ma mngon par byung ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1841: brag phug tu mkha' 'gro ma sems dang ldan pa
NK035(ci)004:1842: la mchod pa gyis shig ces rjes gnang sbyin nas
NK035(ci)004:1843: de nyid du bzhugs su gsol lo de dag ni
NK035(ci)004:1844: sprul pa 'byung dngos kyis bstan pa gnas par byed
NK035(ci)004:1845: pa bstan pa yun ring bar gnas par byed pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1846: nye brgyud bstan pa'o de nas khyad par 'byung ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1847: gnas sangs rgyas rnams kyi 'byung byed gnas 'di nyid
NK035(ci)004:1848: du'ang bstan pa phan pa nyid kyi don du ni
NK035(ci)004:1849: bdag gis re zhig bshad par bya de nas rdo
NK035(ci)004:1850: rje gdan nas byang shar mtshams su dpag tshad lnga
NK035(ci)004:1851: 'das pa na dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal
NK035(ci)004:1852: zhes bya ba mtha' bskor dpag tshad phyed dang gnyis
NK035(ci)004:1853: yod pa ri sa'i lte ba lta bu la khod
NK035(ci)004:1854: snyoms shing lag mthil lta bu la mtha' dang dbus
NK035(ci)004:1855: dang mtho dma' med pa de nyid kyi dbus drang
NK035(ci)004:1856: po na dpal lha las babs pa'i mchod rten zangs
NK035(ci)004:1857: las byas shing gser gyis byugs pa'i 'khor lo gdugs
NK035(ci)004:1858: dang bcas pa dril bu g.yer kha'i sgra sna tshogs
NK035(ci)004:1859: 'byung ba phyogs bzhi nas ston pa'i sku'i mchod rten
NK035(ci)004:1860: re re la rin po che sna tshogs kyi rgyu
NK035(ci)004:1861: las byung ba'o dur khrod de'i byang shar mtshams na
NK035(ci)004:1862: 'jig rten pa'i lha rten dpag bsam gyi shing b+hi
NK035(ci)004:1863: sa la zhes bya ba la dur bya'i tshogs dpag
NK035(ci)004:1864: tu med pa 'bab cing gnas pa 'jig rten gyi
NK035(ci)004:1865: lha ni dga' byed dbang phyug ces bya ba seng
NK035(ci)004:1866: ge nag po la zhon pa lag na mdung rtse
NK035(ci)004:1867: gsum thogs pa dar dmar po'i 'jol ber gyon pa
NK035(ci)004:1868: 'gro ba'i srog len pa la thogs pa med pa
NK035(ci)004:1869: 'khor bye ba dang bcas ba gnas so de na
NK035(ci)004:1870: mkha' 'gro ma dpag tu med pa gnas te la
NK035(ci)004:1871: la ni mig nas nyi ma'i 'od zer 'byung ba
NK035(ci)004:1872: la la ni kha nas 'brug sgra sgrog cing ma
NK035(ci)004:1873: he la zhon pa la la ni lag na gri
NK035(ci)004:1874: thogs shing mig 'bru tshugs su lta ba la la
NK035(ci)004:1875: ni lag na thod pa brtsegs pa thogs shing stag
NK035(ci)004:1876: la zhon pa la la ni lag na mi ro
NK035(ci)004:1877: thogs shing seng ge la zhon pa la la ni
NK035(ci)004:1878: rgyu ma za zhing khyung la zhon pa la la
NK035(ci)004:1879: ni mdung rtse la mi ro bkal zhing lce spyang
NK035(ci)004:1880: la zhon pa la la ni khrag gi rgya mtsho
NK035(ci)004:1881: brlabs shing gdong bcu'am lnga la sogs pa yod pa
NK035(ci)004:1882: la la ni lag pa dpag tu med pa na
NK035(ci)004:1883: sems can gyi rnam pa mang po thogs pa dang
NK035(ci)004:1884: de bzhin du la la ni rang rang gi mgo
NK035(ci)004:1885: bo bcad nas lag tu thogs pa yod pa la
NK035(ci)004:1886: la ni rang gi snying bton nas lag tu bzung
NK035(ci)004:1887: ba dang la la ni rang gi khog pa phye
NK035(ci)004:1888: nas rgyu ma bzung zhing za ba dang la la
NK035(ci)004:1889: ni rta dang glang po che dang ba glang la
NK035(ci)004:1890: zhon pa dpag tu med pa gnas pa'i dbus na
NK035(ci)004:1891: dga' byed kyi mtsho yod pa dur khrod na gnas
NK035(ci)004:1892: pa'i srog chags dpag tu med pa gnas shing 'gro
NK035(ci)004:1893: ba rnams kyis skad cig 'gyu bar mi nus pa
NK035(ci)004:1894: srog dngos su len cing za bar byed pa'i gnas
NK035(ci)004:1895: su shes rab kyi gdul bya la phyin ci log
NK035(ci)004:1896: par byed pa la dgongs nas slob dpon dga' rab
NK035(ci)004:1897: rdo rje nyid kyis der byon te khyab 'jug gi
NK035(ci)004:1898: bu mo skra grol ba gcer bur phyung pa la
NK035(ci)004:1899: zhon nas byon no de nas dur khrod de na
NK035(ci)004:1900: gnas pa'i srog chags rab tu 'jigs pa de dag
NK035(ci)004:1901: gis kyang shing thog ngo mtshar can mang po lhags
NK035(ci)004:1902: shing phul rab tu 'dud do de nas dbus kyi
NK035(ci)004:1903: mchod rten la sku'i rgyab gtad nas mkha' 'gro ma
NK035(ci)004:1904: nyi ma'i 'od zer la sogs pa dpag tu med
NK035(ci)004:1905: pa la chos ston to dus de tsa na rdo
NK035(ci)004:1906: rje gdan gyi nub phyogs na rim pa gnyis pa
NK035(ci)004:1907: zhes bya ba'i grong khyer na bram ze legs ldan
NK035(ci)004:1908: ston pa zhes bya ba dang yum snang ba'i sgron
NK035(ci)004:1909: me zhes bya ba'i bu bstan pa dam pa 'dzin
NK035(ci)004:1910: pa'i bdag po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba rig
NK035(ci)004:1911: pa'i gnas lnga la khyad par du sbyangs pa gcig
NK035(ci)004:1912: yod de de la nam mkha' nas 'jam dpal rnon
NK035(ci)004:1913: pos lung bstan pa dur khrod chen po bzang lung
NK035(ci)004:1914: du lung bstan pa kye rigs kyi bu 'bras bu
NK035(ci)004:1915: tshe gcig lus gcig la sangs rgya bar 'dod na
NK035(ci)004:1916: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal du song zhig
NK035(ci)004:1917: ces lung bstan no de nas 'jam dpal bshes gnyen
NK035(ci)004:1918: gyis dur khrod bsil ba'i tshal du byon nas dga'
NK035(ci)004:1919: rab rdo rje dang zhal mjal ba'i zhu ba phul
NK035(ci)004:1920: bas lo bdun cu rtsa lnga'i bar du sprul pa'i
NK035(ci)004:1921: sku dang lhan cig tu chos nyan to 'di'i dus
NK035(ci)004:1922: na sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas lo lnga
NK035(ci)004:1923: brgya dang bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi lon pa'i dus na
NK035(ci)004:1924: de'i byang shar na chu bo dan tig bya ba'i
NK035(ci)004:1925: mgor dga' rab rdo rje nyid zag pa dang bcas
NK035(ci)004:1926: pa'i phung po mi snang bar byas nas yongs su
NK035(ci)004:1927: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan nas de'i tshe
NK035(ci)004:1928: sa rnam pa drug tu g.yos pa dang 'od zer
NK035(ci)004:1929: gyi phung po dpag tu med pa dang sgra chen
NK035(ci)004:1930: po byung bas 'jam dpal bshes gnyen brgyal zhing sa
NK035(ci)004:1931: la 'gyel lo brgyal sangs nas bltas pas nam mkha'
NK035(ci)004:1932: la 'od phung gi dkyil na bla ma bzhugs pa
NK035(ci)004:1933: mthong nas 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis smre sngags mang
NK035(ci)004:1934: po phyung ba kye ma kyi hud kye ma klong
NK035(ci)004:1935: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na 'jig rten mun
NK035(ci)004:1936: pa gang gis sel zhes lan gsum gyi bar du
NK035(ci)004:1937: brjod pa dang nam mkha' 'od phung gi dkyil 'khor
NK035(ci)004:1938: nas phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo man chad phyung ste
NK035(ci)004:1939: rin po che gsar gyi za ma togs sen gang
NK035(ci)004:1940: ba cig rab tu 'jigs pa'i sgra dang bcas te
NK035(ci)004:1941: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la bskor ba lan gsum du
NK035(ci)004:1942: byas te phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du babs so de
NK035(ci)004:1943: kha phye nas ltas pas dga' rab rdo rje'i tshig
NK035(ci)004:1944: gsum gnad du brdeg pa rin po che lnga'i gzhi
NK035(ci)004:1945: la beed+au r+ya zhun ma'i yi ge rang nan gyi
NK035(ci)004:1946: rgya dang bcas pa cig 'dug go de bltas pa
NK035(ci)004:1947: tsam gyis 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bum pa tshad ldan
NK035(ci)004:1948: nas tshad ldan du bkang ba lta bur gyur to
NK035(ci)004:1949: de yang dga' rab rdo rje chos zad pa'i dus
NK035(ci)004:1950: dang 'jam dpal bshes gnyen nyams 'phel ba'i dus nyid
NK035(ci)004:1951: 'dzom pa'o sprul pa po rang grol ba'i rang snang
NK035(ci)004:1952: ste bstan pa yun ring du gnas par byed pa
NK035(ci)004:1953: sprul pa rang bzhin gyis gnas 'byed do +thii 'khor
NK035(ci)004:1954: lo lta bu sprul pa'i sku la 'dud de nas
NK035(ci)004:1955: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis 'bum tsho dpag
NK035(ci)004:1956: tu med pa'i grangs las rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK035(ci)004:1957: po rnams la sde gsum du phye ste sems gnas
NK035(ci)004:1958: pa rnams la sems kyi sde bya bral rnams la
NK035(ci)004:1959: klong gi sde gnad gtso bo rnams la man ngag
NK035(ci)004:1960: gi sde de las kyang khyad par du bsdus pa
NK035(ci)004:1961: thig le rang gnas du phab pa 'di la snyan
NK035(ci)004:1962: rgyud dang bshad rgyud gnyis su phye nas snyan rgyud
NK035(ci)004:1963: gnyis mchan du btab nas bshad rgyud snying gi ti
NK035(ci)004:1964: ka rnams gtad pa'i gnas ma rnyed nas rdo rje
NK035(ci)004:1965: gdan gyi byang shar mtshams na pha bong rdo rje
NK035(ci)004:1966: rgya gram gyis btab pa'i 'og tu sbas te mkha'
NK035(ci)004:1967: 'gro ma'i rgya dang bcas chos bdag gis rgyas btab
NK035(ci)004:1968: ste mi snang bar byas so de nas rdo rje
NK035(ci)004:1969: gdan nas nub nas rgyang grags gcig na dur khrod
NK035(ci)004:1970: chen po so so'i gling zhes bya ba na mtha'
NK035(ci)004:1971: bskor du dpag tshad gcig yod de de'i dbus na
NK035(ci)004:1972: rang byung gi mchod rten rgya che la srid du
NK035(ci)004:1973: ring ba 'khor lo gdugs dang bya rur bcas pa
NK035(ci)004:1974: rin po che dngul las byas pa dril bu g.yer
NK035(ci)004:1975: kha'i d+r+wa bas rab tu mdzes par spras pa nyi
NK035(ci)004:1976: ma dang zla ba'i rgyan yod pa de'i log rnams
NK035(ci)004:1977: la ke'u ri ma mo brgyad kyi gzugs rang byung
NK035(ci)004:1978: du yod pa'o de'i byang shar na spu gri mun
NK035(ci)004:1979: zhes bya ba'i mtsho yod pa de'i nang na chu
NK035(ci)004:1980: srin la sogs pa'i gdug pa can sna tshogs gnas
NK035(ci)004:1981: pa mtha' ma na sna tshogs 'dul pa'i brag gis
NK035(ci)004:1982: kun bskor ba de'i lho nub mtshams na 'jig rten
NK035(ci)004:1983: lha 'dre ngo mtshar can ni shing lha nag po
NK035(ci)004:1984: nya gro ta chen po zhig la rtse la dur
NK035(ci)004:1985: bya'i tshang yod pa sked pa na dug sbrul nag
NK035(ci)004:1986: po'i tshang yod pa rtsa ba na dur phag nag
NK035(ci)004:1987: po'i tshang yod pa 'jig rten gyi lha rten ni
NK035(ci)004:1988: kun dga' gzhon nu zhes bya ba gdong pa seng
NK035(ci)004:1989: ge la lag pa bzhi na ral gri dang mi
NK035(ci)004:1990: mgo dang mdung shing dang mdung rtse gsum pa la
NK035(ci)004:1991: mi ro bkal ba 'dzin pa thod pa'i phreng bas
NK035(ci)004:1992: lus kun tu brgyan pa dang lus la dar nag
NK035(ci)004:1993: po'i ber gyon pa dang 'khor gsod byed ma mo
NK035(ci)004:1994: 'bum gyis bskor ba glang po la zhon pa rab
NK035(ci)004:1995: tu sha dang khrag la dad pa zhig yod do
NK035(ci)004:1996: der mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs dpag tu med pa yod
NK035(ci)004:1997: de la la ni se ge la zhon cing skra
NK035(ci)004:1998: grol ba thod pa dgu brtsegs kyi rgyal mtshan 'phyar
NK035(ci)004:1999: ba la la ni bya'i tshogs la zhon cing seng
NK035(ci)004:2000: ge'i rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba la la ni lus cig
NK035(ci)004:2001: la gdong bcu cig yod cing rgyu ma dang snying
NK035(ci)004:2002: la sogs pa za ba dang la la ni bud
NK035(ci)004:2003: med nag mo ral pa gsig cing kha nas spyang
NK035(ci)004:2004: khyi 'byung bar byed pa dang la la ni mi'i
NK035(ci)004:2005: lus la gshog pa nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2006: gseb nas gnam lcags kyi thog char 'bebs par byed
NK035(ci)004:2007: pa'o lag na stag gi rgyal mtshan thogs pa la
NK035(ci)004:2008: la ni rang gi lus stod smad 'bral zhing glo
NK035(ci)004:2009: snying 'don pa dang la la ni rang gi yan
NK035(ci)004:2010: lag bcad nas phyogs thams cad du dor ba dag
NK035(ci)004:2011: yod do de ltar rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs ston par
NK035(ci)004:2012: byed pa dpag tu med pa dag yod do de
NK035(ci)004:2013: na dur bya dang dur phag dang dug sprul dang
NK035(ci)004:2014: ce spyang mdog mi 'dra ba mang po dang spyang
NK035(ci)004:2015: ki dang ki li ka dang la sogs pa'o rab
NK035(ci)004:2016: tu 'jigs pa'i bung ba dang ro gsar rnying gi
NK035(ci)004:2017: tshogs dpag tu med pa mang po dang rus pa
NK035(ci)004:2018: dang khrag gi rgya mtsho dang mi mgo'i khang pa
NK035(ci)004:2019: dang thod pa skam po'i khang bu rnam par brtsegs
NK035(ci)004:2020: pa na la la 'brad la la za la la
NK035(ci)004:2021: rgyug la la ngu la la mig 'byin la la
NK035(ci)004:2022: rkang 'cha' rus pa mur rgyu ma la sogs za
NK035(ci)004:2023: ba'i dbus de na rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug rnams
NK035(ci)004:2024: gnas te rnal 'byor pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa
NK035(ci)004:2025: sna tshogs byed pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo yang mang
NK035(ci)004:2026: du rgyu ba na slob dpon chen po 'jam dpal
NK035(ci)004:2027: bshes gnyen seng ge bsnol ba'i khri steng na rdo
NK035(ci)004:2028: rje skyil mo krung du bzhugs te gser dang dngul
NK035(ci)004:2029: dang rma bya la sogs pa'i gdugs phub pa'i rgyal
NK035(ci)004:2030: mtshan sna tshogs bsrang zhing dur khrod khang bu brtsegs
NK035(ci)004:2031: pa na bzhugs shing mkha' 'gro ma'i tshogs kyis yongs
NK035(ci)004:2032: su bskor nas ting nge 'dzin skyong ba la lo
NK035(ci)004:2033: brgya dang rtsa dgu'i bar du snyoms par bzhugs so
NK035(ci)004:2034: dus de tsa na rgya nag po'i yul so sha'i
NK035(ci)004:2035: gling zhes bya ba na yab khyim bdag dge ba
NK035(ci)004:2036: ldan pa'i ming can ces bya dang yum snang ba
NK035(ci)004:2037: gsal ba rab tu mkhyen pa zhes bya ba'i bu
NK035(ci)004:2038: sh+r+ai sing ha zhes bya ba sbyangs pa'i yon tan
NK035(ci)004:2039: dang ldan pa zhig yod de grong khyer sho'ang 'joms
NK035(ci)004:2040: nag po zhes bya bar skyes nas lo bco lnga
NK035(ci)004:2041: lon pa'i tshe na rgya nag po'i byang chub shing
NK035(ci)004:2042: drung rgya nag po'i slob dpon ha ti b+ha la
NK035(ci)004:2043: zhes bya ba las yi ge'i 'gyur dang rtsis dang
NK035(ci)004:2044: sgra dang tshad ma dang bstan bcos dang rig pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2045: gnas rnam pa lnga rnams lo gsum bslabs mkhas pa
NK035(ci)004:2046: rtsod pa med pa cig byung de nas byang chub
NK035(ci)004:2047: shing drung gi nub phyogs grong khyer gser gling bya
NK035(ci)004:2048: bar 'gro snyam nas rnga mong nag mo shin tu
NK035(ci)004:2049: stobs che ba gcig la zhon nas kha nub tu
NK035(ci)004:2050: bltas te phyin pas de nyid kyi bar gyi mtha'
NK035(ci)004:2051: khob kyi nam mkha' la thugs rje chen po spyan
NK035(ci)004:2052: ras gzigs dbang phyug mngon sum du zhal 'dzum pa
NK035(ci)004:2053: mdzad nas bden pa byin pa'i phyag rgya dang ldan
NK035(ci)004:2054: pas nyid la lung bstan pa kyee skal ldan rigs
NK035(ci)004:2055: kyi bu 'bras bu nges par 'dod na ni rgya
NK035(ci)004:2056: gar gyi yul grong khyer so sa'i gling zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:2057: ba yod pas rigs kyi bu der song zhig ces
NK035(ci)004:2058: bya bar lung bstan pas sh+r+ai sing ha nyid rab
NK035(ci)004:2059: tu tshim nas bsam pa cig skyes te bdag ni
NK035(ci)004:2060: da rung na so gzhon pas 'bras bu gsang sngags
NK035(ci)004:2061: de nyid rab tu go sla bar bya ba'i phyir
NK035(ci)004:2062: lo bdun gyi bar du gsang sngags phyi nang mtha'
NK035(ci)004:2063: dag la goms par bya snyam nas de nas slar
NK035(ci)004:2064: rgya nag shar phyogs ri bo rtse lngar phyin nas
NK035(ci)004:2065: gdol ba'i slob dpon bi le ki ti zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:2066: ba la gsang sngags phyi nang du grags pa'i rgyud
NK035(ci)004:2067: dang lung dang man ngag dang sgrub thabs su grags
NK035(ci)004:2068: pa rnams lo bdun gyi bar du shes pas bslabs
NK035(ci)004:2069: so de nas lo bdun cu rtsa gnyis bar la
NK035(ci)004:2070: don med stong par 'dug de nas rgya nag po
NK035(ci)004:2071: so yar tha zhes bya bar rab tu byung nas
NK035(ci)004:2072: lo sum cur khrims srung de nas yang snga dro'i
NK035(ci)004:2073: dus su ri bo rtse lnga'i shar na khrus kyi
NK035(ci)004:2074: rdzing bu dal zhing 'jam pa'i nang na khrus byed
NK035(ci)004:2075: kyin 'dug pa la sh+r+ai sing ha nyid rab tu
NK035(ci)004:2076: 'gyur skad cig tsam dran pa'am shes pa'i nyams 'gags
NK035(ci)004:2077: de nas dran pa sad nas yar langs pas nam
NK035(ci)004:2078: mkha' la 'od kyi phung po'i dkyil na thugs rje
NK035(ci)004:2079: chen po nyid snang bar gyur te yang lung bstan
NK035(ci)004:2080: to de nas sh+r+ai sing ha'i bsam pa la 'di
NK035(ci)004:2081: nas rgya gar yul du 'gro ba la lam la
NK035(ci)004:2082: bar chad kyi sa mang po yod snyam nas rdzu
NK035(ci)004:2083: 'phrul gcig sgrub nas 'gro dgos snyam pas bar der
NK035(ci)004:2084: le lo g.yeng pas lo bcu tsam 'gyangs de nas
NK035(ci)004:2085: lo gsum gyi bar la bsgrubs pas grub pa thob
NK035(ci)004:2086: ste khyad par du tshe la dbang po'i rig 'dzin
NK035(ci)004:2087: grub bo de nas rigs 'dzin gyi rten tshogs pa
NK035(ci)004:2088: la lo bcu dgu lon de nas rgya gar gyi
NK035(ci)004:2089: yul na lo bcu dgu tsa na so sa gling
NK035(ci)004:2090: du rdzu 'phrul la brten nas sa la khru gang
NK035(ci)004:2091: gis ma reg par rlung gis bskyod pa bzhin du
NK035(ci)004:2092: phyin nas 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang mjal te phyag
NK035(ci)004:2093: dang bskor ba dang man+dala 'bul ba dang bla ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2094: bya ba rnams byas shing bdag rjes su gzung bar
NK035(ci)004:2095: zhu ba phul bas gnang ngo de nas lo nyi
NK035(ci)004:2096: shu rtsa lnga'i bar la gdams pa rnams zhus shing
NK035(ci)004:2097: de nyid nyams su blangs so 'di'i dus na sangs
NK035(ci)004:2098: rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas lo brgyad brgya dang
NK035(ci)004:2099: sum cu lon pa'o de dag kyang dur khrod de
NK035(ci)004:2100: nyid kyi dbus kyi mchod rten gyi rtse la 'jam
NK035(ci)004:2101: dpal bshes gnyen kyang zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung
NK035(ci)004:2102: po mi snang bar nam mkha' 'od dang sgras gang
NK035(ci)004:2103: bar snang sa gzhi sil snyan gyis gang zhing mya
NK035(ci)004:2104: ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan te der sh+r+ai sim
NK035(ci)004:2105: ha nyid brgyal zhing sa la 'gyed bar gyur to
NK035(ci)004:2106: brgyal sangs nas bltas pas dam pa nyid 'od phung
NK035(ci)004:2107: gi dkyil na bzhugs pa mthong nas gdung ba'i smre
NK035(ci)004:2108: sngags bton pa kye ma kyi hud kye ma klong
NK035(ci)004:2109: ston pa rdo rje'i 'od nub na 'jig rten mun
NK035(ci)004:2110: pa gang gis sel zhes brjod pas phyag g.yas pa
NK035(ci)004:2111: brkyang ste sh+r+ai sim ha nyid kyi phyag g.yas pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2112: mthil du 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi sgom nyams drug
NK035(ci)004:2113: gi zhal chems rin po che'i za ma tog sen
NK035(ci)004:2114: gang ba cig babs so de zhal phye nas bltas
NK035(ci)004:2115: pas rin po che sna lnga'i shog bu la rin
NK035(ci)004:2116: po che brgya rtsa gcig gis yi ge bris pa
NK035(ci)004:2117: cig 'dug ste de babs pa tsam gyis sh+r+ai sim
NK035(ci)004:2118: ha nyid rtogs pa gding dang ldan par gyur te
NK035(ci)004:2119: bum pa tshad ldan nas tshad ldan du byo ba
NK035(ci)004:2120: bzhin du tshig lhag pa dang chad pa med cing
NK035(ci)004:2121: don la 'khrul pa med par gyur to de'i 'og
NK035(ci)004:2122: tu 'jam dpal bshes gnyen nyid de nas lo sum
NK035(ci)004:2123: brgya nyer lnga na rgya gar gyi nub phyogs gser
NK035(ci)004:2124: gyi me tog gis brgyan pa'i gling zhes bya bar
NK035(ci)004:2125: bardzusa nas skyes te 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma
NK035(ci)004:2126: zhes bya bar grags so de nas o rgyan gyi
NK035(ci)004:2127: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la gsang sngags sgrub sde
NK035(ci)004:2128: mtha' dag gnang ba bstan no de'i 'og tu bstan
NK035(ci)004:2129: pa gser gyi snying po rab tu snang byed 'di
NK035(ci)004:2130: rnal 'byor sgrub pa la brtson pa'i +aar+ya de ba
NK035(ci)004:2131: la bstan no de nyid kyang dur khrod 'jag ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2132: gling zhes bya bar sba mo spungs pa'i ri la
NK035(ci)004:2133: zag bcas mi snang bar yang dag par rdzogs par
NK035(ci)004:2134: sangs rgyas so mchog tu bde ba 'phel bar byed
NK035(ci)004:2135: pa dur khrod kyi gnas 'byed do +thii dpal ldan
NK035(ci)004:2136: ye shes rdzogs pa'i 'khor lo can 'jig rten drug
NK035(ci)004:2137: gi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang rnyed par dka' ba'i
NK035(ci)004:2138: dam pa rje la 'dud de ltar 'jam dpal bshes
NK035(ci)004:2139: gnyen 'das nas sh+r+ai sing has rdo rje gdan gyi
NK035(ci)004:2140: 'og nas gsang ba'i gnad bsdus pa'i gsang sngags rnams
NK035(ci)004:2141: phyung nas rgya nag po'i byang chub shing drung du
NK035(ci)004:2142: sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i gnas su khyer nas phyin te
NK035(ci)004:2143: bstan pa 'byung ba yang dag pa'i yi ge rnams
NK035(ci)004:2144: byang chub shing drung du lha khang gi yang steng
NK035(ci)004:2145: brang khang sbrel mar sh+r+ai sing ha nyid kyis rdzogs
NK035(ci)004:2146: pa chen po thig le'i skor la phyi skor dang
NK035(ci)004:2147: nang skor dang gsang ba'i skor dang gsang ba bla
NK035(ci)004:2148: na med pa'i skor dang bzhir phye nas skor gsum
NK035(ci)004:2149: ni spros bcas kyi don du bsdebs nas lha khang
NK035(ci)004:2150: gi bya 'dab kyi 'og ka ba bzhi sgril gyi
NK035(ci)004:2151: bar du zangs kyi sgrom bu'i nang du bcug ste
NK035(ci)004:2152: phyi rabs kyi don du sbas te mkha' 'gro ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2153: rgya dang chos bdag gi rgyas btab nas bar der
NK035(ci)004:2154: mi snang bar byas so de nas khyad par zab
NK035(ci)004:2155: mo'i gnad gsang ba bla na med pa yongs su
NK035(ci)004:2156: rdzogs pa chen po'i skor ni sh+r+ai sing ha nyid
NK035(ci)004:2157: snying dang gzugs kyi phung po gnyis 'bral ba med
NK035(ci)004:2158: pa de bzhin du nyid kyi lus la rtag tu
NK035(ci)004:2159: bcangs shing yod pa las nam mkha'i gnas la 'thug
NK035(ci)004:2160: po zhig tu gu ru sh+r+ai sing ha nyid kyis
NK035(ci)004:2161: gsang ba'i nyams skyong zhing lus kyi spyod pa skyong
NK035(ci)004:2162: zhing yod pa'i mtshan mo'i rmi lam na sh+r+ai sing
NK035(ci)004:2163: ha'i ma ru byas pa bud med rgyan kun gyis
NK035(ci)004:2164: brgyan pa gcig na re e ma bu gcig longs
NK035(ci)004:2165: dang e sha kye gsang ba yang gsang bsdus pa
NK035(ci)004:2166: snying thig snying po rnams bkra shis khri sgo'i lha
NK035(ci)004:2167: khang gi dkyil du sbos la rang rgyas thob phyi
NK035(ci)004:2168: rabs bstan pa'i btsas su 'gyur ro zhes zer ba
NK035(ci)004:2169: ni mkha' 'gro ma rnam par rol pa'i rgyan ces
NK035(ci)004:2170: bya bas lung bstan pas de nas zhag gsum na
NK035(ci)004:2171: rgya nag po bkra shis khri sgo'i lha khang gi
NK035(ci)004:2172: ka ba'i gseng du sbas te mkha' 'gro ma dang
NK035(ci)004:2173: chos bdag gis rgya rim pa gnyis kyis btab cing
NK035(ci)004:2174: bar der mi snang bar byas so de yang khyad
NK035(ci)004:2175: par du sngags kyi srung ma e ka tsa ti
NK035(ci)004:2176: la gtad de skal ldan snying gi bu dang 'phrad
NK035(ci)004:2177: par shog ces smon lam btab nas mi snang ba
NK035(ci)004:2178: nyid du mdzad do yang rtsis kyi yi ge gto
NK035(ci)004:2179: sbyor gnad kyi rgya chen po dang dngos po sgyur
NK035(ci)004:2180: byed gto'i yi ge dang lha khang du sbas nas
NK035(ci)004:2181: mi snang bar byas so de nas sh+ai sing ha
NK035(ci)004:2182: nyid rgya nag po bsil byed bya ba'i dur khrod
NK035(ci)004:2183: shing ljon pa mang pos yongs su bskor ba de'i
NK035(ci)004:2184: nang rim na shing ka ra b+ai ras bskor ba
NK035(ci)004:2185: de'i nang na smyug ma dang 'dam bu'i tshal yod
NK035(ci)004:2186: pa de'i dbus na ro gas ra rnying gi tshogs
NK035(ci)004:2187: dpag tu med pa yod pa na mkha' 'gro ma
NK035(ci)004:2188: dngos su sgra mang po 'don pa dang sha za
NK035(ci)004:2189: zhing khrag 'thung ba rus pa'i tshogs mang po 'cha'
NK035(ci)004:2190: zhing lding ba dang gzugs mi 'dra ba rnam pa
NK035(ci)004:2191: sna tshogs dang kha dog mi 'dra ba rnam pa
NK035(ci)004:2192: sna tshogs pa dang de bzhin du dung 'bud pa
NK035(ci)004:2193: la sogs pa'i sgra rnam pa sna tshogs 'byin pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2194: dbus na thod pa'i khang bu brtsegs pa rtse la
NK035(ci)004:2195: me 'bar zhing du ba sna tshogs 'thul ba sked
NK035(ci)004:2196: pa na zhag 'dzin cing rtsa ba na klu'i bu
NK035(ci)004:2197: mo dag khrus byed cing yod pa na sh+r+ai sing
NK035(ci)004:2198: ha nyid dgongs pa la gnas te glang po che
NK035(ci)004:2199: rab tu bsnol ba'i khri steng na khyab 'jug gcer
NK035(ci)004:2200: bu bsgyur ba'i steng na rdo rje skyil krung du
NK035(ci)004:2201: bzhugs te de'i tshe lha dang lha min la sogs
NK035(ci)004:2202: pas gdugs dang rgyal mtshan dang ba dan dang dar
NK035(ci)004:2203: gyi lda ldi la sogs pa blangs shing rab tu
NK035(ci)004:2204: 'dud do dus de'i tshe na rgya gar gyi nub
NK035(ci)004:2205: phyogs glang po'i tshal zhes bya ba grong khyer 'bum
NK035(ci)004:2206: tsho rtsa dgu yod pa na yab khyim bdag bde
NK035(ci)004:2207: ldan 'khor lo zhes bya ba dang yum bdag nyid
NK035(ci)004:2208: gsal ma zhes bya ba'i bu bi ma la mi
NK035(ci)004:2209: tra zhes bya ba dang yang rgya gar gyi shar
NK035(ci)004:2210: phyogs ka ma la sh+ai la'i shar gyi grong khyer
NK035(ci)004:2211: na yab gdol pa shan ti lag pa zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:2212: ba dang yum dge ba'i sems ma zhes bya ba'i
NK035(ci)004:2213: bu ye shes mdo bya ba dang gnyis bzhugs so
NK035(ci)004:2214: de'i dus na rgya gar rdo rje gdan na pan+di
NK035(ci)004:2215: ta lnga brgya bzhugs te de rnams kyi nang nas
NK035(ci)004:2216: de gnyis mkhas pa thugs shes rab legs par sbyangs
NK035(ci)004:2217: pa skye ba sngon ma la bral ze swa ta
NK035(ci)004:2218: zhes bya ba'i sras su sku 'khrungs pa de'i tshe
NK035(ci)004:2219: yang skye ba snga ma'i las kyi 'brel ba yod
NK035(ci)004:2220: pas rab tu mthun pa gnyis bzhugs te de'i tshe
NK035(ci)004:2221: rdo rje gdan nas nub kyi rgyang grags na 'dam
NK035(ci)004:2222: bu'i tshal rab tu 'thug cing me tog rab tu
NK035(ci)004:2223: dri zhim pa rnams kyis spras pa yod par dro
NK035(ci)004:2224: thon nas skyo shas skyes te sa 'chag tu byon
NK035(ci)004:2225: pas nam mkha' la sgra gcig grags te steng du
NK035(ci)004:2226: dus gcig la bltas pas dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK035(ci)004:2227: dngos su 'ja' tshon lta bu sku bzhugs te lung
NK035(ci)004:2228: bstan pa kye rigs kyi bu gnyis khyed gnyis kyis
NK035(ci)004:2229: skye ba lnga brgya'i bar du pan+di ta'i lus blangs
NK035(ci)004:2230: nas dam pa'i chos spyad kyang 'bras bu gsang sngags
NK035(ci)004:2231: yang ma thob pas sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob
NK035(ci)004:2232: par 'dod cing tshe 'di nyid la zag pa dang
NK035(ci)004:2233: bcas pa'i phung po mi snang bar 'dod na rgya
NK035(ci)004:2234: nag po'i yul byang chub shing drung gi lha khang
NK035(ci)004:2235: du song dang zhes lung bstan no de ltar lung
NK035(ci)004:2236: bstan pa tsam gyis bi ma la mi tra brtson
NK035(ci)004:2237: 'grus che bas de ka ltar log nas grong khang
NK035(ci)004:2238: nas lhung bzed blangs nas gshegs so de nas rgya
NK035(ci)004:2239: nag po'i yul byang chub shing drung du byon pas
NK035(ci)004:2240: mkhas pa sh+r+ai sing ha dang mjal lo rje dam
NK035(ci)004:2241: pa rab tu mnyes te lo nyi shu'i bar la
NK035(ci)004:2242: snyan brgyud kyi man ngag dang rgyud phyi nang gsang
NK035(ci)004:2243: gsum gyi gdams pa ni gnang ste dpe ni ma
NK035(ci)004:2244: gnang ngo de nas bi ma la thugs tshim nas
NK035(ci)004:2245: slar rgya gar du byon de'i dus na rgya gar
NK035(ci)004:2246: gyi yul dga' byed kyi tshal zhes bya ba'i grong
NK035(ci)004:2247: khyer gyi mthar mkhas pa ye shes mdo dang mjal
NK035(ci)004:2248: bas ye shes mdo dran pa rnyed nas bi ma
NK035(ci)004:2249: la de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa bzhugs kyin gda'
NK035(ci)004:2250: 'am zhes bsnyad pas bi ma la'i zhal nas bzhugs
NK035(ci)004:2251: kyin gda' 'o zhes gsungs so ye shes mdo'i thugs
NK035(ci)004:2252: la bdag ni brtson 'grus re chung snyam nas de
NK035(ci)004:2253: nyid rang rgya nag po'i yul du byon nas rang
NK035(ci)004:2254: bzhin gyi byin brlabs kyis zla ba dgu'i lam la
NK035(ci)004:2255: nyin gcig gis chod par phyin te byang chub shing
NK035(ci)004:2256: drung gi mdun du byon nas bla ma mi bzhugs
NK035(ci)004:2257: pas ye shes mdo yid 'khrugs te phyogs kun tu
NK035(ci)004:2258: bltas kyang gang na'ang mi 'dug pas thugs dgongs la
NK035(ci)004:2259: sngar bi ma lar gang na bzhus ma dris snyam
NK035(ci)004:2260: nas bzhugs pa las gzhan gang yang ma mthong bar
NK035(ci)004:2261: bud med nag mo shin tu ldem bag chags pa
NK035(ci)004:2262: chu'i ban rgyab na khur ba so dung so 'khor
NK035(ci)004:2263: mar 'dug pa smin ma g.yu'i smin ma bar ma
NK035(ci)004:2264: chad par 'dug pa dpral ba'i dkyil na gnyer ma
NK035(ci)004:2265: rdo rje gyen la langs pa gcig yod pa shin
NK035(ci)004:2266: tu mdangs dang ldan pa lag na g.yu'i ne tsho
NK035(ci)004:2267: thogs pa gcig na re kyee skal ba dang ldan
NK035(ci)004:2268: pa dam pa nges pa'i lung 'dod na bkra shis
NK035(ci)004:2269: khri sgor khyod rang la snang bar 'gyur ro zhes
NK035(ci)004:2270: mkha' 'gro ma mgon sems byams ma zhes bya bas
NK035(ci)004:2271: lung bstan no de nas ye shes mdo nyid kyis
NK035(ci)004:2272: rgya nag po'i dbus bkra shis khri sgo zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:2273: ba'i grong khyer chen po gcig la sgo shar sgo
NK035(ci)004:2274: ru bltas pas stong phrag phyed dang gsum lho sgor
NK035(ci)004:2275: bltas pas phyed dang gsum nub dang byang du bltas
NK035(ci)004:2276: pas de tsam re re khri phrag gcig yod pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2277: dbus na lha khang gcig yod pa lha khang de
NK035(ci)004:2278: la yang lha'i khang pa brtsegs pa lha'i gtso 'khor
NK035(ci)004:2279: mi 'dra ba khri phrag gcig yod pa de na
NK035(ci)004:2280: dge slong gi dge 'dun khri phrag re re yod
NK035(ci)004:2281: pa rta dang glang po la sogs pa'i khri phrag
NK035(ci)004:2282: re re yod pa bya dang rol mo ba rnams
NK035(ci)004:2283: kyang de snyed ci yod pa khri sgo zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:2284: ba der byon nas yang bla ma dang ma mjal
NK035(ci)004:2285: te thugs rab tu 'gyur te bdag ni bsod nams
NK035(ci)004:2286: re chung skal pa rang med pa cig yin snyam
NK035(ci)004:2287: ste yang bla ma dang ma mjal snyam pa la
NK035(ci)004:2288: lha khang de'i byang shar gyi mtshams kyi bya 'dab
NK035(ci)004:2289: kyi steng na lus seng ge la mgrin pa rma
NK035(ci)004:2290: bya ru 'dug pa gdong sdig gdong du yod pa
NK035(ci)004:2291: lus la thig le sna tshogs pas brgyan pa lag
NK035(ci)004:2292: na thod pa sum brtsegs kyi dbyug pa thogs pa
NK035(ci)004:2293: gcig na re e ma bu khyod skal ldan pas
NK035(ci)004:2294: bla ma da ci'i bar la dan ti'i yul du
NK035(ci)004:2295: gshegs khyod ni rab ldan skal che bas da ni
NK035(ci)004:2296: byang phyogs drang po na bsil byed ces bya'i dur
NK035(ci)004:2297: khrod yod de nas mkha' 'gro brtse bar ldan las
NK035(ci)004:2298: can 'du ba'i khyad par yod bu khyod song zhig
NK035(ci)004:2299: der song la ci bde bar ni gsang sngags mnos
NK035(ci)004:2300: zhes gsungs so de ni mkha' 'gro ma spyod ma
NK035(ci)004:2301: zhes bya bas lung bstan nas de nyid du byon
NK035(ci)004:2302: pas sh+r+ai sing ha dang zhal mjal nas rin po
NK035(ci)004:2303: che'i man+dala phul nas phyag dang bskor ba byas nas
NK035(ci)004:2304: bdag rjes su gzung du gsol zhes zhus pas thod
NK035(ci)004:2305: pa'i khang bu brtsegs pa'i nang nas khyab 'jug gcer
NK035(ci)004:2306: bu'i gdan las bzhengs te ci'ang mi gsung bar phyag
NK035(ci)004:2307: gi sor mi gsum gyen la bslangs nas spyan nam
NK035(ci)004:2308: mkha' la gzigs so de'i tshe ye shes mdo'i thugs
NK035(ci)004:2309: dgongs la lo gsum nas gnang ba yin nam snyam
NK035(ci)004:2310: pas sh+r+ai sing ha nyid kyis mkhyen nas dbu gug
NK035(ci)004:2311: pa lan gsum mdzad nas de nas ye shes mdos
NK035(ci)004:2312: lo gsum bar la man+dala phul ba dang bku mnye
NK035(ci)004:2313: dang dril phyis dang phyag rten la sogs pa bla
NK035(ci)004:2314: ma'i bya ba ci rigs pa byed kyin bzhugs so
NK035(ci)004:2315: de nas lo gsum lon pa'i tshe na yang ye
NK035(ci)004:2316: shes mdos sh+r+ai sing ha la phyag dang bskor ba
NK035(ci)004:2317: byed cing gser phye ma srang sum cu so brgyad
NK035(ci)004:2318: phul nas bla mas bdag rjes su gzung bar zhu
NK035(ci)004:2319: zhes zhus pas gnang ngo lo dgu'i bar la snyan
NK035(ci)004:2320: brgyud las ma gnang ngo de'i tshe ye shes mdo
NK035(ci)004:2321: bsam pa gcig skyes te gdams ngag 'di'i 'gro so
NK035(ci)004:2322: 'di la dpe gcig yod du thang snyam pa la
NK035(ci)004:2323: yang zhus pas byang chub shing drung nas dpe rnams
NK035(ci)004:2324: bton nas gnang ngo bshad rgyud de dag gi gdams
NK035(ci)004:2325: pa yang lo bcu gcig gi bar la gcod de
NK035(ci)004:2326: nas ye shes mdo nyid thugs tshim ste yid rangs
NK035(ci)004:2327: par gyur pa'i tshe sh+r+ai sing ha'i zhal nas khyod
NK035(ci)004:2328: yid rab tu tshim mam gsungs pas ye shes mdos
NK035(ci)004:2329: bdag ni yid rab tu tshim zhes zhus pas bla
NK035(ci)004:2330: ma'i zhal nas gtad pa med gsungs pas ye shes
NK035(ci)004:2331: mdo rtog pa gcig skyes te da gdams ngag 'di
NK035(ci)004:2332: la lam khyer rab tu zab pa'i gdams ngag cig
NK035(ci)004:2333: yod 'dug ang snyam nas yang zhus pas bla ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2334: zhal nas 'di la dbang bskur cig thob dgos gsungs
NK035(ci)004:2335: nas bkra shis khri sgo'i lha khang gi nang du
NK035(ci)004:2336: phyi spros bcas kyi dbang rdzogs par gnang nas de
NK035(ci)004:2337: nas gsang ba bla na med pa'i man ngag rnams
NK035(ci)004:2338: lo gsum gyi bar la gnang ngo bla ma'i zhal
NK035(ci)004:2339: nas 'di rnams la dpe tshan gcig yod de khyod
NK035(ci)004:2340: rang dus la babs tsa na gnang bar 'gyur gyi
NK035(ci)004:2341: gsungs nas gdams pa'i sna kha phal cher rdzogs par
NK035(ci)004:2342: mdzad do de nas ye shes mdo'i thugs dgongs la
NK035(ci)004:2343: gdams ngag ni zhus thag chod rgya gar du 'agro'am
NK035(ci)004:2344: snyam pa la bsam pa phyis skyes te yul du
NK035(ci)004:2345: 'gro bas don med sangs rgya ba'i gdams ngag ni
NK035(ci)004:2346: yod 'di rang du nyams su len cing bla ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2347: zhabs tog bya snyam ste bla ma la zhu phul
NK035(ci)004:2348: bas bdag ni nyams su len par zhu zhes zhus
NK035(ci)004:2349: pas bla ma'i zhal nas khyod nyams su len pa
NK035(ci)004:2350: la dbang rdzogs par byed dgos pas 'di dum bu'i
NK035(ci)004:2351: lugs bya ba yin gsungs nas grong khyer stong pa
NK035(ci)004:2352: zhig tu spros med kyi dbang rdzogs par gnang de
NK035(ci)004:2353: nas lo gcig na ri bo chen po ko sa
NK035(ci)004:2354: li zhes bya ba'i rtse mo la 'khor 'das ru
NK035(ci)004:2355: shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa tshar bar byas te shin
NK035(ci)004:2356: tu spros pa med pa'i dbang rdzogs par mdzad nas
NK035(ci)004:2357: yang nges shes thun mong ma yin pa skyes so
NK035(ci)004:2358: de nas zla ba gcig lon pa'i dus na rab
NK035(ci)004:2359: tu spros pa med pa'i dbang rdzogs par mdzad nas
NK035(ci)004:2360: rang sems la dbang thob bo de nas lo bcu
NK035(ci)004:2361: drug tu bla ma'i mdzad spyod lta zhing nyams su
NK035(ci)004:2362: blangs so de dag gi dus su sh+r+ai sing ha
NK035(ci)004:2363: nyid skabs su brtul zhugs rlung 'dzin gyi spyod pa
NK035(ci)004:2364: mdzad skabs su khyad par gyi spyod pa stag dang
NK035(ci)004:2365: ma he la zhon cing sku lus gcer bu la
NK035(ci)004:2366: khrag dang zhag gis byugs pa dbu la ral pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2367: thor tshugs chen po la sgro sna tshogs pa btsugs
NK035(ci)004:2368: te phyag g.yas pa na ral gri bzung g.yon pa
NK035(ci)004:2369: na thod pa khrag gis bkang ba zhal du gsol
NK035(ci)004:2370: zhing dur khrod rnams su rgyu ba dang res glang
NK035(ci)004:2371: po che la zhon nas lus la stag gi pags
NK035(ci)004:2372: pa gyon pa dang phyag na d+aa ma ru dkrol
NK035(ci)004:2373: zhing srid pa spyi lugs kyi zhwa gyon pa dur
NK035(ci)004:2374: khrod du rgyu ba la sogs pa'i spyod pa sna
NK035(ci)004:2375: tshogs pa mdzad do res 'ga' sa chu me rlung
NK035(ci)004:2376: gi rten 'brel du ma yang 'gro ba rnams la
NK035(ci)004:2377: phan pa'i don du mdzad do de nas dus de'i
NK035(ci)004:2378: tshe sh+r+ai sing ha nyid li'i rgyal po dpal spyin
NK035(ci)004:2379: ces bya bas spyan drangs te seng ge dkar mo
NK035(ci)004:2380: yan lag drug dang ldan pa la dar gyi khang
NK035(ci)004:2381: bu phub ste de'i steng du dar gyi gdugs sum
NK035(ci)004:2382: brtsegs phub ste gnod sbyin gyi bu stobs dang ldan
NK035(ci)004:2383: pa drug gis rkang pa bteg ste gshegs so de
NK035(ci)004:2384: ltar gshegs nas zhag bdun lon pa'i nang par sgra
NK035(ci)004:2385: chen po zhig grags te ye shes mdos bltas pas
NK035(ci)004:2386: nam mkha' 'od phung gi dkyil na dam pa nyid
NK035(ci)004:2387: bzhugs pa mthong ste brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel lo
NK035(ci)004:2388: brgyal sangs tsa na nam mkha' 'od phung gi dkyil
NK035(ci)004:2389: snang bar gyur pa bar snang thams cad la sgra'i
NK035(ci)004:2390: tshogs snyan par dka' ba dpag tu med pa grags
NK035(ci)004:2391: pa dang sa gzhi thams cad rab tu ldeg pa
NK035(ci)004:2392: dang 'gul ba dang 'khyom pa'i stengs na gser dang
NK035(ci)004:2393: dngul la sogs pa'i me tog sil ma dpag tu
NK035(ci)004:2394: med pa spungs pa dag mthong ste bdag gi bla
NK035(ci)004:2395: ma mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan snyam nas
NK035(ci)004:2396: gdung ba'i smre sngags phyung ba kye ma kyi hud
NK035(ci)004:2397: kye ma klong ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na
NK035(ci)004:2398: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel zhes brjod pa
NK035(ci)004:2399: dang sh+r+ai sing ha nyid kyi zhal chems gzer bu
NK035(ci)004:2400: bdun pa phyag gi mthil du babs pa dang sgra
NK035(ci)004:2401: yang snying thig gsang ba'i man ngag rnams bkra shis
NK035(ci)004:2402: khri sgor ka ba'i bsam le'u nang na yod kyi
NK035(ci)004:2403: longs la dur khrod b+ha sing gi gnas la song
NK035(ci)004:2404: zhig ces lung bstan no 'di'i dus su sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)004:2405: mya ngan las 'das nas lo dgu brgya dang brgyad
NK035(ci)004:2406: cu rtsa bzhi lon mchog tu sems ba skyed par
NK035(ci)004:2407: byed pa dur khrod kyi gnas 'byed do sku gsum
NK035(ci)004:2408: ye shes lnga ldan pa'i mkhyen bdag ye shes can
NK035(ci)004:2409: la 'dud de nas ye shes mdo'i dgongs pa la
NK035(ci)004:2410: bla ma'i lung bzhin bya'o snyam nas gsang ba'i dpe
NK035(ci)004:2411: rnams bton nas dpe rnams thams cad chu dar gyi
NK035(ci)004:2412: ldeb la dril nas rgya nag po'i mi 41le smin
NK035(ci)004:2413: tshogs bdag bya ba dang sems bzang dpal gros bya
NK035(ci)004:2414: ba gnyis la bskur te rgya gar gyi yul dur
NK035(ci)004:2415: khrod b+ha sing zhes bya bar byon no dur khrod
NK035(ci)004:2416: de ni rdo rje gdan nas shar phyogs thag shin
NK035(ci)004:2417: tu ring ba na yod de de'i byang gi phyogs
NK035(ci)004:2418: na ri nag po glang po che nyal ba lta
NK035(ci)004:2419: bu'i kha nas chu 'bab pa dang lho nas stag
NK035(ci)004:2420: ser po langs pa lta bu'i ri las tsan+dana gor
NK035(ci)004:2421: shi sha'i dri 'thul ba dang nub nas seng ge
NK035(ci)004:2422: gnam la mchongs ba lta bu'i ri brag la bya
NK035(ci)004:2423: khyung gi tshang yod pa shar na tshangs pa lha'i
NK035(ci)004:2424: zhal lta bu'i li shing la dgos 'dod gang yang
NK035(ci)004:2425: 'byung ba'i dbus na bsod nams rdzogs pa'i mchod rten
NK035(ci)004:2426: ces bya ba rgyu rin po che zangs dang lcags
NK035(ci)004:2427: las byas pa srog shing tsan+dana sbrul gyi snying po
NK035(ci)004:2428: can la rtse mo shing 'dab sna tshogs pad+ma bkram
NK035(ci)004:2429: pa lta bu'i gdugs su gyur pa sked par rin
NK035(ci)004:2430: po che mthon mthing gi 'khor lo brtsegs pa lta
NK035(ci)004:2431: bu'i 'khor lo bris pa rtsa bar pad+ma'i snying po
NK035(ci)004:2432: kha sbyar ba lta bu'i bar rim gyi ngos la
NK035(ci)004:2433: yod pa bang rim tha ma'i steng na shing gi
NK035(ci)004:2434: rgyal po seng d+ha zhes bya ba phyogs kun nas
NK035(ci)004:2435: yod de shing de'i yal ga thams cad gcig la
NK035(ci)004:2436: gcig 'brel te g.yu thag 'brel ba lta bu'i d+r+wa
NK035(ci)004:2437: ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa lta bur gyur pa
NK035(ci)004:2438: bang rim 'og ma rnams na dur khrod na gnas
NK035(ci)004:2439: pa'i srog chags du ma yod pa de'i stengs na
NK035(ci)004:2440: lha'i bu mo mang pos bskor bar byed pa de'i
NK035(ci)004:2441: steng ma na bsil byed thogs pa'i dge bsnyen ma
NK035(ci)004:2442: mang pos bskor ba byed pa de'i steng na sprul
NK035(ci)004:2443: pa'i bya rigs mang bskor ba byed pa'o de nyid
NK035(ci)004:2444: nas lho drang po'i rgyang grags phyed na 'jig rten
NK035(ci)004:2445: pa'i lha rten shel gyi khang pa sgo yod pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2446: nang na gshin rje dus mtshams bya ba mdog nag
NK035(ci)004:2447: la skra g.yengs shing mche ba gtsigs pa gsus pa
NK035(ci)004:2448: che la mig gyen du ldog pa 'jig rten gyi
NK035(ci)004:2449: ma mo stong gis bskor ba gnas so de'i steng
NK035(ci)004:2450: du 'dzam bu'i gling bskyod par byed pa'i lha btsun
NK035(ci)004:2451: d+ha ri zhes bya gnas te de yang mdog dmar
NK035(ci)004:2452: po gcer bu bong bu zhon pa khrag gi ral
NK035(ci)004:2453: pas sa gzhi khengs pa mig nas du ba 'thul
NK035(ci)004:2454: ba kha nas me 'bar ba lag pa g.yas pa
NK035(ci)004:2455: na mdung rtse gsum pa la mi ro rgyang thabs
NK035(ci)004:2456: su bkal ba lag pa g.yon pa na bum pa
NK035(ci)004:2457: 'dzin pa de la bdud kyi 'khor brgyad brgyas bskor
NK035(ci)004:2458: ba las su gson khrag 'jigs pa dam tshig nyams
NK035(ci)004:2459: pa'i gshed ma zhig yod de dur khrod de na
NK035(ci)004:2460: ro gsar rnying gi tshogs dpag tu med pa gcig
NK035(ci)004:2461: gi steng na gcig chags pa dpag tu med pa
NK035(ci)004:2462: yod pa dur khrod de na gnas pa'i srog chags
NK035(ci)004:2463: de dag ni shing gi 'bras bu sna tshogs dpag
NK035(ci)004:2464: tu med pa la longs spyod pa sha khrag la
NK035(ci)004:2465: mi dad pa'o de'i phyogs mtshams na mi mgo rlon
NK035(ci)004:2466: pa'i khang pa na shar na mkhas pa dpal gyi
NK035(ci)004:2467: blo gros zhes bya ba khyung la zhon cing khams
NK035(ci)004:2468: gsum kun tu 'gro bar byed pa mdog smug nag
NK035(ci)004:2469: la gdong lnga pa ral pa'i thor tshugs gyen du
NK035(ci)004:2470: 'khyil ba'i gseb na thod pa'i phreng bas yongs su
NK035(ci)004:2471: bskor ba phyag bcu na 'khor lo dang pad+ma dang
NK035(ci)004:2472: mdung shing zhing chung mda' gzhu thogs pa'o g.yon na
NK035(ci)004:2473: dge slong dang seng ge dang spyang khyi dang ba
NK035(ci)004:2474: dan dang gzhu la sogs pa'i las la dur khrod
NK035(ci)004:2475: kyis brgyan pa 'khor zhi ba'i rigs kyi mkha' 'gro
NK035(ci)004:2476: ma stong gnas so lho na mkha' 'gro ma mgon
NK035(ci)004:2477: sems ma mdog ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa
NK035(ci)004:2478: tshogs bdag la zhon pa gcer bu 'jigs pa'i gzugs
NK035(ci)004:2479: can g.yu dang mu men gyi gshog pa yod pa
NK035(ci)004:2480: g.yas na thod pa'i nang na phag mo'i chang gis
NK035(ci)004:2481: bkang ba g.yon dngos grub kyi gzugs bsnams pa mig
NK035(ci)004:2482: 'bru tshugs su lta zhing zhal bgrad pa rgyas pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2483: mkha' 'gro ma stong gis bskor ba yod do yang
NK035(ci)004:2484: nub na 'bar ma chen mo mdog dmar mo skra
NK035(ci)004:2485: bardzesa pa gcer bu la g.yas rdo rje g.yon zhags
NK035(ci)004:2486: pa rkyang ba ri dwags la zhon pa 'khor dbang
NK035(ci)004:2487: gi rigs kyi mkha' gro ma stong gis bskor ba
NK035(ci)004:2488: yod do byang na kun tu bzang mo mdog ljang
NK035(ci)004:2489: gu gcer bu skra grol ba g.yas 'ug pa g.yon
NK035(ci)004:2490: khra thogs pa spyang ki la zhon pa 'khor las
NK035(ci)004:2491: kyi mkha' 'gro ma stong gis bskor ba'o byang shar
NK035(ci)004:2492: na me khyer glog gi 'phreng ba 'dzin pa zhes
NK035(ci)004:2493: bya ba sku mdog ljang ba gcer bu skra bardzesa
NK035(ci)004:2494: pa g.yas pa na ral gri'i phreng ba g.yon na
NK035(ci)004:2495: sdigs mdzub ma he la zhon pa la gsod pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2496: ma mo bdun gyis bskor ba shar lho na sha
NK035(ci)004:2497: ba ri sngo sangs gcer bu skra grol ba lag
NK035(ci)004:2498: pa gnyis kyis bam chen bzung ste za bar byed
NK035(ci)004:2499: pa glang po la zhon pa sgrol bar byed pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2500: ging mo bdun gyis bskor ba lho nub na grags
NK035(ci)004:2501: sbyin mo sngo skya gcer bu skra'i mdud pa rgyab
NK035(ci)004:2502: tu bcings pa lag pa na seng ge'i rgyal mtshan
NK035(ci)004:2503: 'dzin pa kha nas h+aum zhes sgrog pa ro la
NK035(ci)004:2504: zhon pa zla ba'i 'od yod pa sha za ma
NK035(ci)004:2505: mo bdun gyis bskor ba'o nub byang na chags med
NK035(ci)004:2506: ma mdog smug nag skra gcig g.yas nas g.yon du
