NK035(ci)004:2507: 'khyil ba mig gcig gis stong gsum dus gcig la
NK035(ci)004:2508: mthong ba so gcig gis dam nyams kyi srog rtsa
NK035(ci)004:2509: gcod pa lag pa gcig gis nad kyi rkyal pa
NK035(ci)004:2510: dus gcig la 'dzin pa nu ma gcig gis 'gro
NK035(ci)004:2511: ba rnams dus gcig la gsos pa rkang pa gcig
NK035(ci)004:2512: gis 'khor 'das rnams dus gcig la 'khor ba dang
NK035(ci)004:2513: sha dang khrag la dad pa dang 'chi bdag gi
NK035(ci)004:2514: ma mo bdun gyis bskor ba gnas so de la
NK035(ci)004:2515: byol song gi rigs dpag tu med pa dang sprul
NK035(ci)004:2516: pa'i ma mo dpag tu med pa gnas so de
NK035(ci)004:2517: dag gi lho na lte ba rin po che khri
NK035(ci)004:2518: rkang brtsegs pa'i steng na stag grus ma la chibs
NK035(ci)004:2519: nas de yang de nyid kyi steng na skyil krung
NK035(ci)004:2520: du bzhugs nas phyag mchog sbyin mdzad pa rma bya'i
NK035(ci)004:2521: gdugs phub nas phyogs kun nas ba dan dang bsil
NK035(ci)004:2522: g.yab la sogs pa bslangs pa'i dbus na ye shes
NK035(ci)004:2523: mdo nyid bzhugs te mkha' 'gro ma rnams la gsang
NK035(ci)004:2524: ba snying thig bka' gsang nges pa rnams ston to
NK035(ci)004:2525: de'i tshe na bi ma la mi tra nyid dur
NK035(ci)004:2526: khrod tha chung zhes bya bar glang sngon po zhig
NK035(ci)004:2527: la ni zhon lag tu bsil g.yab kyi gdugs gcig
NK035(ci)004:2528: bzung bla gos phrag pa yas la gzar nas spyod
NK035(ci)004:2529: pa la byon pa'i tshe nam mkha' las mkha' 'gro
NK035(ci)004:2530: ma dpal gyi blo gros zhes bya bas lung bstan
NK035(ci)004:2531: pa kye skal ldan snga ma bas zab pa'i snying
NK035(ci)004:2532: thig gi gdams pa bzhed na dur khrod chen po
NK035(ci)004:2533: b+ha sing gi nags la song zhig ces bya ba
NK035(ci)004:2534: lung bstan pas bi ma la rab tu brtson 'grus
NK035(ci)004:2535: che bas de nyid rang du dur khrod b+ha sing
NK035(ci)004:2536: du byon pas sngar gyi mkhas pa ye shes mdo
NK035(ci)004:2537: bzhugs kyin 'dug pas mos pa thun mong ma yin
NK035(ci)004:2538: pa skyes te sngar gyi mnyam po la bla ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2539: slob ma sngon yin kyang che chung ma brtsis par
NK035(ci)004:2540: phyag dang bskor ba byas nas kye dam pa lags
NK035(ci)004:2541: sngon chad dang mi 'dra ba'i gdams pa mnga' bar
NK035(ci)004:2542: gda' bas bdag rjes su gzung du gsol zhes zhu
NK035(ci)004:2543: ba phul bas dbu gug mdzad pas mdzod spu'i bu
NK035(ci)004:2544: ga nas 'od zer 'dom dgu brgya dang dgu bcu
NK035(ci)004:2545: rtsa lnga spros so de yang ngo mtshar skyes so
NK035(ci)004:2546: dam pa'i zhal nas de lta bu la ngo mtshar
NK035(ci)004:2547: rgyu med gsungs nas spyan nam mkha' la ldog pas
NK035(ci)004:2548: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i zhing khams kyis nam mkha'
NK035(ci)004:2549: khengs pa tsam sprul nas dam pa sangs rgyas sprul
NK035(ci)004:2550: pa de la ni gdams pa'i rigs mi 'dra ba
NK035(ci)004:2551: dpag tu med pa bzhugs kyin 'dug khong zag bcas
NK035(ci)004:2552: kyi phung po mi snang bar yongs su mya ngan
NK035(ci)004:2553: las 'das sngon chad ma yin pa'i man ngag ngo
NK035(ci)004:2554: mtshar can 'ba' zhig yod pas rigs kyi bu dang
NK035(ci)004:2555: bas rab tu 'dun pa'i sgo nas dbang bzhi rab
NK035(ci)004:2556: tu rdzogs par gyis shig gsungs nas de nyid du
NK035(ci)004:2557: spros bcas kyi dbang rdzogs par mdzad de nyid thob
NK035(ci)004:2558: pa'i rtags su mdzod spu'i bu ga rab tu gsal
NK035(ci)004:2559: bar gyur to de nas lo gcig lha'i khang pa
NK035(ci)004:2560: zhig tu spros med kyi dbang bskur de nyid thob
NK035(ci)004:2561: pa'i rtags su ba spu'i bu ga rnams rlangs ba
NK035(ci)004:2562: du ba lta bur byung de nas zla ba drug
NK035(ci)004:2563: gi bar la ri bo srod byed kyi rtse mo
NK035(ci)004:2564: la 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa tshar
NK035(ci)004:2565: bar spyad do shin tu spros med kyi dbang rdzogs
NK035(ci)004:2566: par bskur de nyid du nyams su myong ba thun
NK035(ci)004:2567: mong ma yin pa bskyed do de nyid thob pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2568: rtags su shangs kyi rtse mo la yi ge a
NK035(ci)004:2569: dkar po thigs la khyad pa cig byung de nas
NK035(ci)004:2570: zla ba drug na rab tu spros med kyi dbang
NK035(ci)004:2571: rdzogs par bskur bas sems nyid ngo bo zang thal
NK035(ci)004:2572: du mthong ngo de'i dus na mkhas pa chen po
NK035(ci)004:2573: de gnyis kyis lo brgya brgya dang gsum gsum lon
NK035(ci)004:2574: te dbang dang po bskur ba'i dus skor gsum gyi
NK035(ci)004:2575: gdams ngag dpe dang bcas pa gnang ngo gnyis pa
NK035(ci)004:2576: gsang ba bla na med pa'i dpe rgyud gnang gsum
NK035(ci)004:2577: pa de dag gi zhal gdams rnams gnang bzhi pa
NK035(ci)004:2578: snying tig gsungs pa'i gnad bsdus pa mtha' dag ma
NK035(ci)004:2579: lus par gnang ngo lo bcu bzhi'i bar la gdams
NK035(ci)004:2580: pa zhun thag bcad do de'i dus su sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)004:2581: mya ngan las 'das nas lo dgu brgya dang dgu
NK035(ci)004:2582: bcu rtsa bzhi lon no de'i dus su ye shes
NK035(ci)004:2583: mdo nyid kyang zag bcas mi snang bar yongs su
NK035(ci)004:2584: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan te lhag ma
NK035(ci)004:2585: med par nam mkha' 'od kyis bkang ste gshegs pas
NK035(ci)004:2586: bi ma la mi tra brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel
NK035(ci)004:2587: lo brgyal sangs nas bltas pas nam mkha' 'od phung
NK035(ci)004:2588: gi dkyil na bla ma bzhugs nas bar snang thams
NK035(ci)004:2589: cad lha rdzas kyi gdugs dang rgyal mtshan dang ba
NK035(ci)004:2590: dan la sogs pas gang ba sa gzhi thams cad
NK035(ci)004:2591: lha dang mi'i bye brag gis khengs pa dag mthong
NK035(ci)004:2592: ste gdung ba'i smre sngags phyung ba kye ma kyi
NK035(ci)004:2593: hud kye ma klong ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub
NK035(ci)004:2594: na 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel zhes brjod
NK035(ci)004:2595: pas phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo man chad phyung ste
NK035(ci)004:2596: bi ma la'i phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du rin po
NK035(ci)004:2597: che'i za ma tog gi nang du rin po che
NK035(ci)004:2598: sna lngas rgyas btab ste de babs pa tsam gyis
NK035(ci)004:2599: kyang bi ma la nyid kyang bum pa tshad ldan
NK035(ci)004:2600: nas tshad ldan du byo ba ltar tshig la lhag
NK035(ci)004:2601: chad med don la 'khrul pa med par gyur to
NK035(ci)004:2602: ma smin pa smin par byed pa dur khrod kyi
NK035(ci)004:2603: gnas 'byed do +thii s+ya mya s+ya sam mkha' 'gro
NK035(ci)004:2604: ma'i tshogs kyis bskor yang dag lam du 'gro 'dzud
NK035(ci)004:2605: pa 'jigs pa rnams las rgya cher sgrol dam pa
NK035(ci)004:2606: sangs rgyas gshegs la 'dud de nas mkhas pa bi
NK035(ci)004:2607: ma mi tras rgya gar shar phyogs ka ma ru'i
NK035(ci)004:2608: grong khyer na rgyal po seng ge bzang po zhes
NK035(ci)004:2609: bya ba'i mchod gnas lo nyi shu mdzad do de'i
NK035(ci)004:2610: dus na smyug ma'i bsil khang du bzhugs shing zas
NK035(ci)004:2611: gos dang bral yang rgyal po de'i tshogs sogs pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2612: phyir bzhugs so rgyal po de yang slob dpon mkhas
NK035(ci)004:2613: pa de'i byin rlabs kyis rang bzhin gyis bsam gtan
NK035(ci)004:2614: phebs pa'am 'khor dang longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa'am
NK035(ci)004:2615: yul khams tsam du yang bkra shis pa'i yan lag
NK035(ci)004:2616: dang ldan par gyur te de nas rgya gar gyi
NK035(ci)004:2617: nub phyogs grong khyer bi rgya la zhes bya bar
NK035(ci)004:2618: rgyal po d+har+m+aa pa la zhes bya ba'i chos ston
NK035(ci)004:2619: gsol zhing nang nub rgyal po'i tshogs gsog pa'i phyir
NK035(ci)004:2620: chos ston la snyag go de nas dpag tshad lnga
NK035(ci)004:2621: brgya yod pa 'das pa'i byang phyogs na dur khrod
NK035(ci)004:2622: rab tu snang byed ces bya ba yod de shin
NK035(ci)004:2623: tu nags 'thug pa zhig gi dkyil na spang gshongs
NK035(ci)004:2624: dpag tshad gcig yod de de'i dbus na rnam par
NK035(ci)004:2625: rgyal ba 'khor ba 'jig ces bya ba'i mchod rten
NK035(ci)004:2626: khri lcags las byas pa bang rim ni zangs dang
NK035(ci)004:2627: mu men dang gser las byas pa pad+ma rin po
NK035(ci)004:2628: che'i ze la smyug las byas pa bum pa rin
NK035(ci)004:2629: po che mthon mthing las byas pa bre rin po
NK035(ci)004:2630: che phra men las byas pa 'khor lo rnams rin
NK035(ci)004:2631: po che sna mi 'dra ba bcu gsum las byas
NK035(ci)004:2632: pa gdugs rin po che sna tshogs 'dus pa'i 'khrigs
NK035(ci)004:2633: pa las gyur pa nyi zla dang bya ru la
NK035(ci)004:2634: sogs pa rang bzhin gyi rnam dag chen po las
NK035(ci)004:2635: rab tu byung ba'o de'i tha ma na chu'i 'obs
NK035(ci)004:2636: yod pa chu de dag gi nang na klu'i phrug
NK035(ci)004:2637: gu rnams dag byed kyi khrus byed pa de'i lho
NK035(ci)004:2638: nub na 'jig rten pa'i lha rten ni smyug ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2639: phung po 'dra ba'i rnam pa dang d+r+wa bas yongs
NK035(ci)004:2640: su bskor ba'i nang ma matshe'u g.yu'i man+dala lta bu'i
NK035(ci)004:2641: steng na gser gyi bye ma brdal ba lta bu'i
NK035(ci)004:2642: kha dog ser po sprin gyi thog na mthing shun
NK035(ci)004:2643: gyi gur phub pa'i nang na klu'i rgyal po sa
NK035(ci)004:2644: srung zhes bya mdog ser po mgo la sbrul mgo
NK035(ci)004:2645: bdun pa gdengs ka'i dbus na yid bzhin gyi nor
NK035(ci)004:2646: bu rin po che yod pa lag pa gnyis na
NK035(ci)004:2647: bum pa dang sbrul zhags thogs pa chu srin sngon
NK035(ci)004:2648: po la zhon pa 'khor klu'i rigs brgyad kyis bskor
NK035(ci)004:2649: ba rtag tu sems can la rnam par 'tshe bar
NK035(ci)004:2650: byed pa zhig yod de dur khrod de na ni
NK035(ci)004:2651: mkha' 'gro ma la la dmar mo khrag gi ral
NK035(ci)004:2652: pa gsig cing rwa dung 'bud pa la la ni
NK035(ci)004:2653: li dung zhon nas sngon mo g.yu'i go cog gyon
NK035(ci)004:2654: cing lag na mi ro 'dzin pa la la ni
NK035(ci)004:2655: stag la zhon cing gdong dkar mo la khyung gi
NK035(ci)004:2656: gshog pa yod cing lag na rin po che'i bum
NK035(ci)004:2657: pa nor gyis bkang ba thogs pa la la ni
NK035(ci)004:2658: srin mo ral pa snyigs pa gcer bu mo mtshan
NK035(ci)004:2659: nas bu skyes pa la zhon pa mdog dmar skya
NK035(ci)004:2660: dung gi gdugs 'dzin cing kha nas kus 'debs pa
NK035(ci)004:2661: la sogs pa'i mkha' 'gro ma dngos su dpag tu
NK035(ci)004:2662: med do 'dir yang mkha' 'gro ma rang bzhin gyi
NK035(ci)004:2663: stobs kyi gling gzhan gyi ro rnams kyang rang bzhin
NK035(ci)004:2664: gyis 'dir 'du ba'i sha za ba dang khrag 'thung
NK035(ci)004:2665: ba dang rus pa mur ba dang glo snying dang
NK035(ci)004:2666: nang khrol za ba la sogs pa dpag tu med
NK035(ci)004:2667: pa'o stag dang seng ge la sogs pa'i gcan gzan
NK035(ci)004:2668: dpag tu med pa rnams dang kam ka dang lim
NK035(ci)004:2669: du la sogs pa 'dab chags dpag tu med pa
NK035(ci)004:2670: rnams kyang sha dang khrag la dad cing 'dun pa
NK035(ci)004:2671: sha stag go dur khrod der nyin mo dang mtshan
NK035(ci)004:2672: mo brtul zhugs lam du slong ba'i spyod pa rtse
NK035(ci)004:2673: gcig tu mdzad do stag la zhon nas mdung rtse
NK035(ci)004:2674: gsum pa bsnams nas spyod pa mdzad do res ma
NK035(ci)004:2675: he la zhon nas ro'i rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba dang
NK035(ci)004:2676: res glang po che la zhon nas ba dan dmar
NK035(ci)004:2677: po 'phyar ba dang res ce sbyang la zhon nas
NK035(ci)004:2678: phyag gnyis na ral gri 'dzin pa dang res ling
NK035(ci)004:2679: du dang 'ug pa'i tshogs la zhon nas phyag gnyis
NK035(ci)004:2680: na gdugs gnyis bzung nas spyod pa mdzad pa'o de
NK035(ci)004:2681: dag gi dus na sku mdog dang cha lugs bsgyur
NK035(ci)004:2682: ba ni mkha' 'gro ma dbang du sdud pa la
NK035(ci)004:2683: dgongs pa'o skabs su de lta bu'i spyod pa mdzad
NK035(ci)004:2684: cing snying thig gdams pa 'di la lo bdun nyams
NK035(ci)004:2685: su blangs pas rig pa nyid tshad la phebs te
NK035(ci)004:2686: slar 'pho ba chen po'i skur bzhengs nas gang zag
NK035(ci)004:2687: sum stong rim gyis sangs rgya ba'i thabs la gtso
NK035(ci)004:2688: bor mdzad do de'i 'og tu rgyal po de'i don
NK035(ci)004:2689: chos ston cing dur khrod der seng ge la zhon
NK035(ci)004:2690: nas dbu drug la phyag bcu gnyis su sprul nas
NK035(ci)004:2691: phyag rnams na gdugs bzung ba dang khyung la zhon
NK035(ci)004:2692: cing lus seng ger sprul pa'i spyod pa yang lo
NK035(ci)004:2693: bcu gsum du mdzad do de dag gi 'og tu
NK035(ci)004:2694: dur khrod snang byed du gsang ba mchog gi dpe
NK035(ci)004:2695: 'di rnams tshar gsum du bris nas dpe tshar gcig
NK035(ci)004:2696: nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul rgya mtsho gser gyi
NK035(ci)004:2697: bye ma brdal ba'i gling du klu'i rgyal po rnams
NK035(ci)004:2698: la gtad nas phyi rabs kyi skal ldan rnams kyi
NK035(ci)004:2699: don du smon lam btab nas sbas te bar der
NK035(ci)004:2700: mi snang bar byas so dpe tshar gcig kha che'i
NK035(ci)004:2701: yul gyi mtha' 'khob rig lngan ces bya bar grong
NK035(ci)004:2702: khyer gyi mtha' ma na gser gyi gling zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:2703: ba'i brag gi skyibs la mkha' 'gro ma 'du ba'i
NK035(ci)004:2704: gnas su phyi rabs kyi skal ldan rnams kyi don
NK035(ci)004:2705: du mkha' 'gro ma rnams la gtad nas chos bdag
NK035(ci)004:2706: gi rgya dang bka' rtags dang gnyis btab nas bar
NK035(ci)004:2707: der mi snang bar byas so dpe tshar gcig dur
NK035(ci)004:2708: khrod de nyid na smyug ma'i bsil khang na bzhugs
NK035(ci)004:2709: shing bshags pa'i rten mdzad pa dang dur khrod de
NK035(ci)004:2710: na gnas pa'i mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi sgrib pa
NK035(ci)004:2711: dag par byed pa'i don du bzhugs te de nyid
NK035(ci)004:2712: du bzhugs pas dus dus su lha'i bu rnams kyis
NK035(ci)004:2713: mchod pa'i sprin gtibs pa dang sil snyan gyi sgra
NK035(ci)004:2714: sgrog pa dang me tog gi rigs mi 'dra ba'i
NK035(ci)004:2715: char 'bebs pa dang bar snang la bkra shis kyi
NK035(ci)004:2716: tshigs su bcad pa mi 'dra ba mang po sgrog
NK035(ci)004:2717: pa dang de bzhin du klu'i rgyal po dang gnod
NK035(ci)004:2718: sbyin dang nam mkha' lding la sogs pas me tog
NK035(ci)004:2719: dang 'bras bu dang 'dab ma yis brgyan pa'i shing
NK035(ci)004:2720: rnams dang rin po che sna tshogs char 'bebs par
NK035(ci)004:2721: byed de ltar yang dag pa'i bka' phyin ci ma
NK035(ci)004:2722: log pa de'i rang bzhin gyi byin gyi rlabs kyis
NK035(ci)004:2723: yul phyogs de tsam du'ang nad dang mu ge la
NK035(ci)004:2724: sogs pa mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad rgyun chad
NK035(ci)004:2725: do 'dod cing 'dun pa dur khrod kyi gnas 'byed
NK035(ci)004:2726: do +thii sa ma y+aa rgya rgya rgya mkha' 'gro
NK035(ci)004:2727: mi zad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro zhing dpa' bo brtul
NK035(ci)004:2728: zhugs spyod pa'i thabs la mkhas gdul bya'i rgyud sbyong
NK035(ci)004:2729: mkha' 'gro kun 'dul ba dpal ldan spyod pa mdzad
NK035(ci)004:2730: pa'i sku la 'dud de ltar yang spyir 'dzam bu'i
NK035(ci)004:2731: gling na mkha' 'gro ma 'du bar nges pa'i dur
NK035(ci)004:2732: khrod chen po brgya dang bcu gsum yod pa la
NK035(ci)004:2733: rgya gar yul na sum cu rtsa gnyis yod pa
NK035(ci)004:2734: la byed pa'i gnas drug dang nyams skyong ba'i gnas
NK035(ci)004:2735: bcu bzhi dang dam tshig skyong ba'i gnas brgyad dang
NK035(ci)004:2736: 'dod cing 'dun pa drag po bskyed pa'i gnas bzhi
NK035(ci)004:2737: ste sum cu rtsa gnyis yod pa la rang bzhin
NK035(ci)004:2738: gyi mkha' 'gro ma'i gtso mo gnas pa'i gnas brgyad
NK035(ci)004:2739: las med do de ltar brgyad na mchod rten re
NK035(ci)004:2740: chu re 'jig rten pa'i lha drag po re slob
NK035(ci)004:2741: dpon re 'dod pa'i ri re yod 'jig rten pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2742: lha de dag la sgrub thabs re yod pa dang
NK035(ci)004:2743: ma mo re la sgrub thabs re yod pa ni
NK035(ci)004:2744: shin tu zab pa yin no o rgyan gyi yul
NK035(ci)004:2745: na brgyad yod do kha che'i yul na bcu yod
NK035(ci)004:2746: do li dang hor na lnga tsha ba dmar thag
NK035(ci)004:2747: dang dung gi yul na lnga mi nyag dang za
NK035(ci)004:2748: hor gyi yul na bcu 'thon mi dang gar bsam
NK035(ci)004:2749: gyi yul na bcu rgya gar gyi yul na sum
NK035(ci)004:2750: cu rtsa gnyis yod do bod na mkha' 'gro ma
NK035(ci)004:2751: 'du bar nges pa'i gnas gnyis las med de dbu
NK035(ci)004:2752: ru gzho'i ti sgro'i brag dkar po la las kyi
NK035(ci)004:2753: mkha' 'gro ma res 'du res mi 'du ba'i ma
NK035(ci)004:2754: mo bdun gnas so kong po'i lho nub mtshams na
NK035(ci)004:2755: glo dang rdo'i bar na byar po nas nyi ma
NK035(ci)004:2756: bdun na ts+aa ri ts+aa gong zhes bya ba ye
NK035(ci)004:2757: shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma 'du bar nges pa la
NK035(ci)004:2758: bcu gcig brgal ba'i mgo na mkha' 'gro ma khrus
NK035(ci)004:2759: byed pa'i mtsho zhes bya ba 'o ma'i rnam pa
NK035(ci)004:2760: lta bu dkar ba sngo dmar gyi ri mo yod
NK035(ci)004:2761: ba de'i dbus na rin po che las byas pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2762: mchod rten bkra shis sgo mang gi sgo bdun cu
NK035(ci)004:2763: rtsa bdun na dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa bdun gyi
NK035(ci)004:2764: sku shel las grub pa yod pad+ma'i phreng ba la
NK035(ci)004:2765: zhi ba'i lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yod pa bang
NK035(ci)004:2766: rim 'og ma la dpal khrag 'thung lha dgu'i dal
NK035(ci)004:2767: yod pa steng ma la 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi
NK035(ci)004:2768: lha sum brgya'i dkyil 'khor yod pa de'i steng ma
NK035(ci)004:2769: na ma rgyud kyi lha rnams yod pa bang rim
NK035(ci)004:2770: dgu la don gyi gsang sngags kyi nang du grags
NK035(ci)004:2771: pa'i lha rnams yod pa bum pa na khrag 'thung
NK035(ci)004:2772: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor yod pa bre
NK035(ci)004:2773: la gsang 'dus kyi lha rnams yod pa 'khor lo
NK035(ci)004:2774: dang gdugs dang bya ru la sogs pas rab tu
NK035(ci)004:2775: brgyan pa'o der ni dus gnyan gyi dus su mkha'
NK035(ci)004:2776: 'gro ma rnams kyis tsan+dana dkar po'i char 'bebs pa
NK035(ci)004:2777: dag yin no de ma yin pa mkha' 'gro ma'i
NK035(ci)004:2778: gzugs dang gnas sa dang bya ba'i rim pa dang
NK035(ci)004:2779: dngos grub ji ltar thob pa'i bshad pa sa'i lam
NK035(ci)004:2780: yig gi rim pa ni yod do la re brgal
NK035(ci)004:2781: ba'i brtson yang mkha' 'gro ma'i gnas phra mo re
NK035(ci)004:2782: yod do de dag la gzugs ston pa dang /
NK035(ci)004:2783: sgra sgrogs dang h'u h'u zhes zer ba yod do
NK035(ci)004:2784: 'dir ni dad pa can lus dang srog mi lta
NK035(ci)004:2785: ba'i tshe phyi ma dang du len pa'i gang zag
NK035(ci)004:2786: skyes bu zhig gis phyin nas mtsho'i zam pa legs
NK035(ci)004:2787: par rnyed par byas nas bskor ba lan gsum byas
NK035(ci)004:2788: pa tsam gyis phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos
NK035(ci)004:2789: grub thob pa la the tshom med do rgya gar
NK035(ci)004:2790: gyi dur khrod dngos de rnams rnyed na yang de
NK035(ci)004:2791: bzhin no rgya gar gyi dur khrod na mi ma
NK035(ci)004:2792: yin mang po yod do dur khrod dngos de rnams
NK035(ci)004:2793: ni shin tu rnyed par dka' bas lam gyi yi
NK035(ci)004:2794: ge dam pas shes so ming mi 'dra ba ni
NK035(ci)004:2795: dpag tu med pa yod dur khrod dngos de dag
NK035(ci)004:2796: tu ro'i tshogs su kyang ma bskyal bar 'adu'o ro
NK035(ci)004:2797: skyel ba'i dur khrod de rnams na mi ma yin
NK035(ci)004:2798: drag po tshogs te phal cher bar chod 'byung ngo
NK035(ci)004:2799: dngos kyi dur khrod de rnams su phyin pa tsam
NK035(ci)004:2800: gyis mchog gi dngos grub thob par nges so de
NK035(ci)004:2801: dag ni slob dpon grub pa thob pa rgyun ma
NK035(ci)004:2802: chad par bzhugs nges so dur khrod kyi grangs nges
NK035(ci)004:2803: kyi gnas 'byed do pan+di ta chen po bi ma
NK035(ci)004:2804: la'i zhal snga nas dang lo ts+aa ba ska cog
NK035(ci)004:2805: gnyis kyis bsam yas dbu rtse ris gsum gyi bar
NK035(ci)004:2806: khang du bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o
NK035(ci)004:2807: +thii zhes lo rgyus dang po las gnas 'byed bdun
NK035(ci)004:2808: pa rig 'dzin brda'i brgyud pa gtan la phab pa'o
NK035(ci)004:2809: gang zag snyan brgyud pa la 'gyur ba med do
NK035(ci)004:2810: rdzogs so tshig brgyud spros pa gcod pa'i lha la
NK035(ci)004:2811: phyag 'tshal lo da ni gang zag snyan khung brgyud
NK035(ci)004:2812: pa'i gtam rgyud ngo mtshar can ston te de la
NK035(ci)004:2813: gang zag ni gsum ste sprul pa'i gang zag dang
NK035(ci)004:2814: lam la dbang ba'i gang zag dang mos pas gcod
NK035(ci)004:2815: pa'i gang zag go sprul pa'i gang zag ni rje
NK035(ci)004:2816: blon rin po che la sogs pa'o gang zag gi
NK035(ci)004:2817: lus ltar sems can gyi lus su sprul pa tsam
NK035(ci)004:2818: du zad pa las yang dag par sangs rgyas pa
NK035(ci)004:2819: yin pa'o lam la dbang ba'i gang zag ni grub
NK035(ci)004:2820: pa thob zin pa rnams so mos pas gcod pa
NK035(ci)004:2821: ni sgrub par 'dod pa rnams so gang zag ces
NK035(ci)004:2822: bya ba ni zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung po
NK035(ci)004:2823: la rnam par dag pa'i ye shes gang zhig rgyas
NK035(ci)004:2824: nas yod pa ste de nyid tshig rgyud 'khrul pa
NK035(ci)004:2825: med pa la brten nas 'di nyid la zag pa
NK035(ci)004:2826: mi snang bar sangs rgya bar byed do de ltar
NK035(ci)004:2827: byas pas nyon mongs pa'i zag pa la sogs pa
NK035(ci)004:2828: rnams zad par byed pa'o snyan ni rna ba'i dbang
NK035(ci)004:2829: po phyin ci ma log pas tshig gi sgros lhag
NK035(ci)004:2830: pa dang chad pa med par tshig tu shes pa
NK035(ci)004:2831: dang don rang gi rgyud la brten nas tha ma
NK035(ci)004:2832: tshig gi sgro 'dogs chod par byed pa'o brgyud pa'i
NK035(ci)004:2833: dgongs pa la yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)004:2834: ston pa chos kyi sku nas da ltar gyi rnal
NK035(ci)004:2835: 'byor pa bdag yan chad du tshig la lhag chad
NK035(ci)004:2836: med cing sgros ma nor ba dang gang zag mi'i
NK035(ci)004:2837: tshig gis bsnan phri ma byas par thog ma las
NK035(ci)004:2838: mang nyung med par gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa
NK035(ci)004:2839: ni dper na mi mang po'i lag tu gser gyi
NK035(ci)004:2840: pa tra shin tu legs pa gcig brgyus kyang de
NK035(ci)004:2841: nyid bsnan phri med par tha ma gcig gi lag
NK035(ci)004:2842: tu rdol ba dang 'dra bar tshig rgyud la lhad
NK035(ci)004:2843: ma zhugs pas bum pa tshad ldan nas tshad ldan
NK035(ci)004:2844: du byo ba ltar lhag chad med par khengs pa
NK035(ci)004:2845: dang 'dra bar b+hud+d+ha nas rig 'dzin dang da lta'i
NK035(ci)004:2846: yo gi yan chod dgongs pa mnyam zhing lhag chad
NK035(ci)004:2847: med par bsdur thub pas na man ngag rab tu
NK035(ci)004:2848: zab pa'i rtags yon no de lta bu'i man ngag
NK035(ci)004:2849: gsang chen nges pa de su la brgyud na dus
NK035(ci)004:2850: de tsam na rgya gar gyi yul ser skya'i grong
NK035(ci)004:2851: khyer na rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu d+hi chung ba ces
NK035(ci)004:2852: bya ba chos skyong mgon po byams pa'i sprul pa
NK035(ci)004:2853: gcig la mchod gnas pan+di ta lnga brgya bzhugs te
NK035(ci)004:2854: de dag gi nang nas mkhas shing grub pa thob
NK035(ci)004:2855: pa / bi ma la mi tra 'pho ba'i skur
NK035(ci)004:2856: bzhengs pa gcig khyad par du mchod gnas lo drug
NK035(ci)004:2857: cu'i bar la mdzad pa zhig bzhugs so de tsam
NK035(ci)004:2858: na bod kyi yul na rgyal po byang chub sems
NK035(ci)004:2859: dpa' 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi sprul pa khri srong lde'u
NK035(ci)004:2860: btsan zhes bya bas dpal bsam yas lhun gyis grub
NK035(ci)004:2861: pa'i gzhal yas khang bzhengs shing dam pa'i chos dar
NK035(ci)004:2862: zhing rgyas par mdzad pa zhig dang de'i mchod gnas
NK035(ci)004:2863: myang ting 'dzin bzang po zhes bya ba lo bdun
NK035(ci)004:2864: dang zla ba bdun gyi bar la zhi gnas rtse
NK035(ci)004:2865: gcig tu gnas pa sha'i spyan rnam par dag pas
NK035(ci)004:2866: gling bzhi dus gcig la gzigs pa zhig bzhugs te
NK035(ci)004:2867: myang ban chen po de'i zhal nas rje la 'di
NK035(ci)004:2868: skad bgros te kye rgyal po lags rgya gar gyi
NK035(ci)004:2869: yul ser skya'i grong khyer na rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu
NK035(ci)004:2870: ti zhes bya ba la pan+di ta lnga brgya mchod
NK035(ci)004:2871: gnas su bzhugs par gda' bas de dag gi nang
NK035(ci)004:2872: nas 'bras bu gsang sngags la mkhas pa gcig spyan
NK035(ci)004:2873: drangs nas bod kyi rgyal khams su gsang sngags kyi
NK035(ci)004:2874: bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par bagyi'o zhes bsnyad pas
NK035(ci)004:2875: rgyal po yang rab tu mnyes nas de ltar bgyi
NK035(ci)004:2876: gsungs nas de tsam na bod kyi rgyal khams na
NK035(ci)004:2877: blo rno ba dbu ru 'phan yul gyi ska ba
NK035(ci)004:2878: pa na ska ba blo brtan dang 'gro bzang rdo
NK035(ci)004:2879: rje lcam gyi bu ska ba dpal brtsegs zhes bya
NK035(ci)004:2880: ba dang ru lag shab kyi dar sgong nas cog
NK035(ci)004:2881: ro rgyal 'byung dang 'bro gza' mdzes ma'i bu cog
NK035(ci)004:2882: ro klu'i rgyal mtshan zhes bya ba gnyis gcig tu
NK035(ci)004:2883: bsags nas li gar da'i skyems drangs dbu la rin
NK035(ci)004:2884: po che'i prog zhu bkon nas rgyal pos bka' bsgo
NK035(ci)004:2885: ba kye rigs kyi bu rdzu 'phrul lce la dbang
NK035(ci)004:2886: thob pa gnyis 'o skol bod kyi rgyal khams su
NK035(ci)004:2887: 'bras bu gsang sngags rab tu zab ba'i bstan pa
NK035(ci)004:2888: dar bar bya ba'i phyir rgya gar gyi yul ser
NK035(ci)004:2889: skya'i grong khyer na rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti zhes
NK035(ci)004:2890: bya ba la mchod gnas pan+di ta lnga brgya bzhugs
NK035(ci)004:2891: par 'dug pas de'i spyan sngar song la gser gyi
NK035(ci)004:2892: pa tra bdun po 'di phul gser phye bre dgu
NK035(ci)004:2893: po 'di phul la 'di bod kyi rgyal pos skyes
NK035(ci)004:2894: su bskur bas skyes lan du pan+di ta mkhas pa
NK035(ci)004:2895: mchog tu 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi chos la mkhas
NK035(ci)004:2896: pa gcig bardzonga bar zhu zhes brjod la song zhig
NK035(ci)004:2897: ces rgyal pos bka' bsgo bas lo ts+aa ba gnyis
NK035(ci)004:2898: pos rgyal po'i bka' byung bas rgya gar yul du
NK035(ci)004:2899: phyin te rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti la phyag mdzad
NK035(ci)004:2900: nas sngar rgyal po'i gser gyi pa tra dang gser
NK035(ci)004:2901: phye rnams phul te sngar gyi 'phrin byas pas rgyal
NK035(ci)004:2902: po rab tu dgyes nas bod byang chub sems dpa'
NK035(ci)004:2903: gnyis bsil khang 'dir bzhugs shig zer nas pan+di ta
NK035(ci)004:2904: rnams gro la byon pa'i dus su gro gsol ba'i
NK035(ci)004:2905: gral la rgyal po des kye mkhas pa chen po
NK035(ci)004:2906: rnams bdag la bod kyi rgyal pos skyes shin tu
NK035(ci)004:2907: bzang ba gcig bskur byung bas de'i skyes lan du
NK035(ci)004:2908: pan+di ta mkhas pa mchog tu 'bras bu gsang sngags
NK035(ci)004:2909: kyi chos la mkhas pa gcig thong zer gtang 'tshal
NK035(ci)004:2910: zhes bsgo bas slob dpon b+hud+d+ha gu h+ya'i zhal nas
NK035(ci)004:2911: de skad zer ba'i skyes skyel ba de gang na
NK035(ci)004:2912: gda' 'dir khrid la shog dang gsungs nas rgyal pos
NK035(ci)004:2913: khrid nas 'ongs pas lo ts+aa ba gnyis kyis bi
NK035(ci)004:2914: ma la'i sku'i mtshan rtags rnams mthong bas mos pa
NK035(ci)004:2915: rab tu skyes te yar gyi tsho yang spyan dus
NK035(ci)004:2916: cig la bi ma la gzigs mar gyi tsho yang
NK035(ci)004:2917: yar gzigs pa bye ma las mkhyen nas bzhengs pas
NK035(ci)004:2918: g+ha g+ha pa ri zhes pa'i sgra brjod pas lo
NK035(ci)004:2919: ts+aa ba gnyis la tshig go lugs gnyis byung ste
NK035(ci)004:2920: cog ros gzhu mo dag la brten pa'i mda' skyes
NK035(ci)004:2921: bu'i mthe mos rtsol phod na mda' yis pha rol
NK035(ci)004:2922: skyes bar 'gyur zhes bya bar go ska bas gru
NK035(ci)004:2923: bo dag la brten pa'i mis mnyes pa'i skya bas
NK035(ci)004:2924: rtsol phod na mi yis rgya mtsho'i pha rol sgrol
NK035(ci)004:2925: zhes tshig tha dad la don gcig tu go nas
NK035(ci)004:2926: bi ma la la zhus pas bye ma la la
NK035(ci)004:2927: bsten pa yi rgyal po khyod kyis gtong phod na
NK035(ci)004:2928: ngas bod la phan thogs te 'ong gsungs nas rab
NK035(ci)004:2929: tu zab pa gsang ba snying thig gi dpe tshar
NK035(ci)004:2930: gcig dang bcas te +aa tsar+ya sa'i snying po bya
NK035(ci)004:2931: ba g.yog por khrid nas byon pas de'i mtshan mo
NK035(ci)004:2932: rmi lam thams cad kyang 'khrugs rgya gar yul tsam
NK035(ci)004:2933: gyi me tog dang 'bras bu dang shing dang lo
NK035(ci)004:2934: tog thams cad bod du song ba rmi ba dang
NK035(ci)004:2935: nyi zla bod kyi phyogs su song ba rmi ba
NK035(ci)004:2936: dang de'i tshe dur khrod bsil ba tshal gyi mkha'
NK035(ci)004:2937: 'gro ma rnams cho nge 'debs pa 'dug pa dang
NK035(ci)004:2938: rgyal po'i chu tshod dang dbyug gu'i rtsis thams cad
NK035(ci)004:2939: 'khrugs te nang par gyi dus su rgyal po'i pho
NK035(ci)004:2940: brang gi sgo mdun du rgya gar gyi mi thams
NK035(ci)004:2941: cad 'dus nas rmi lam bsdur bar kun mthun te
NK035(ci)004:2942: 'di cis lan gyes pas la la na re ci
NK035(ci)004:2943: zer la la na re ci zer bas bud med
NK035(ci)004:2944: gcig na re rgyal po mdun du spyan drongs dang
NK035(ci)004:2945: rgyal po'i mchod gnas bod la shor ram snga ltas
NK035(ci)004:2946: ni pan+di ta mkhas pa gcig gis 'bras bu gsang
NK035(ci)004:2947: sngags kyi chos brtsams nas dpe tsam med pa yin
NK035(ci)004:2948: pas rgyal po la dris pas kha rtsang bye ma
NK035(ci)004:2949: la bod du shor zer bas rgya gar gyi mi
NK035(ci)004:2950: rnams kyis rkang mgyogs bardzangasa nas /
NK035(ci)004:2951: bod kyi lung mdo dang srang mdo thams cad du
NK035(ci)004:2952: mdo byang btags te bod kyi ban+de gnyis kyis mtha'i
NK035(ci)004:2953: mon bu phra men gyi ngan sngags khyer nas song
NK035(ci)004:2954: bas bod kyi rgyal khams rnams phung ngo zhes mdo
NK035(ci)004:2955: byang mang po btags pas dus de tsam na bi
NK035(ci)004:2956: ma la mu tra spyan drangs nas dpal bsam yas
NK035(ci)004:2957: su byon te lo ts+aa ba gnyis kyis ngo so
NK035(ci)004:2958: bcas pas rgyal po la pan+di ta ni grub pa
NK035(ci)004:2959: thob cing 'pho ba'i skur slar sems can don du
NK035(ci)004:2960: bzhengs pa spyir sde snod ma lus pa mkhyen cing
NK035(ci)004:2961: mchog tu 'bras bu gsang sngags la thugs kyis dgongs
NK035(ci)004:2962: rgyal po rgya gar du dpe tsam yang ma bzhag
NK035(ci)004:2963: par bod du bsnams nas byon nas mchis so zhes
NK035(ci)004:2964: bsnyad pas rgyal po'i zhal nas do nub bu tshal
NK035(ci)004:2965: gser khang du bzhugs dang nang par gro gang du
NK035(ci)004:2966: mos pa dang spro ba bya'o gsungs nas bu tshal
NK035(ci)004:2967: du bzhugs so dus de tsam na bod kyi blon
NK035(ci)004:2968: po gdug pa can rnams kyis mdo byang bklag pa
NK035(ci)004:2969: dang bsam yas su pan+di ta byon no zhes thos
NK035(ci)004:2970: nas blon po rnams kyis spyan sngar 'dug nas 'o
NK035(ci)004:2971: skol gyi 'di na mtha'i mon bu phra men gyi
NK035(ci)004:2972: ngan sngags sna tshogs pa khyer ba yod gda' rgyal
NK035(ci)004:2973: pos bka' chad gsol la 'dir ma bzhag par zhu
NK035(ci)004:2974: ba phul te nang par lo ts+aa ba gnyis kyis
NK035(ci)004:2975: rgyal po'i sku mdun phyin te zhal mjal bar zhu
NK035(ci)004:2976: zhes bsnyad pas rgyal po'i zhal nas khyed gnyis kyi
NK035(ci)004:2977: de pan+di ta gsha' ma min par 'dug phra men
NK035(ci)004:2978: gyi ngan thabs sna tshogs khyer ba yin par 'dug
NK035(ci)004:2979: pas zhag 'ga' mtshan brtag go gsungs nas ma gnang
NK035(ci)004:2980: ngo de nas lo ts+aa ba gnyis rab tu sdug
NK035(ci)004:2981: bsngal zhing zhag gsum bu tshal du nyal ba'i nang
NK035(ci)004:2982: ma gcig bi ma la bzhengs nas rnam par snang
NK035(ci)004:2983: mdzad gzugs kyi lha gzugs kyi lha la ye shes
NK035(ci)004:2984: lha yis phyag bagyi'o zhes phyag mdzad pas der lder
NK035(ci)004:2985: bzo rnams thal bar phung gis song bas lo ts+aa
NK035(ci)004:2986: ba gnyis ngo mtshar skyes nas rgyal po la bsnyad
NK035(ci)004:2987: pas 'o de kun phra men gyi ngan thabs yin
NK035(ci)004:2988: gsungs nas yang lo ts+aa gnyis sems rab tu ma
NK035(ci)004:2989: bde ste bdag cag gnyis kyis rgya gar tsam nas
NK035(ci)004:2990: dka' las spyad nas mkhas pa ngo mtshar 'di lta
NK035(ci)004:2991: bu spyan drangs pa la rgyal po 'di ci yin
NK035(ci)004:2992: snyam nas thugs mug go de nas yang zhag gsum
NK035(ci)004:2993: gyi nang par bzhengs nas rnam par snang mdzad gzugs
NK035(ci)004:2994: kyi lha gzugs kyi lha la ye shes lha yis
NK035(ci)004:2995: dbang bskur ro sa phung la dbu zhwa phud nas
NK035(ci)004:2996: bskon pas sku gzugs sngon ma bas rab tu legs
NK035(ci)004:2997: pa rgya gar gyi lugs su byung ste gzim dngas
NK035(ci)004:2998: dang ldan par gyur nas yang lo ts+aa ba gnyis
NK035(ci)004:2999: kyi rgyal po bsnyad pas de nas rgyal po thugs
NK035(ci)004:3000: ches te 'o na bod kyi rgyal khams su rkang
NK035(ci)004:3001: mgyogs bardzangasa nas zla ba gcig gi tshes gsum gyi
NK035(ci)004:3002: nyin par 'dus shig par btang nas de nas zla
NK035(ci)004:3003: gcig gi nang par dbu rtse rigs gsum sgo mdun
NK035(ci)004:3004: du g.yas su rgyal po la g.yu khri rab tu
NK035(ci)004:3005: 'phang mtho ba brtsigs g.yon du gser spram gyi khri
NK035(ci)004:3006: rab tu 'phangs mtho ba brtsigs bod kun 'dus nas
NK035(ci)004:3007: rgyal pos pan+di ta la phyag mdzad pas rgyal po'i
NK035(ci)004:3008: thugs kar dar men gyi dkyil na rigs gsum mgon
NK035(ci)004:3009: po'i lha bkra yal le 'dug pa kun gyis mthong
NK035(ci)004:3010: ste de ltar 'dug pas bi ma las dbu'i rin
NK035(ci)004:3011: po che prog zhu la +aahmh'u zhes se gol brdabs
NK035(ci)004:3012: pas rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su kun gyis bkra yal
NK035(ci)004:3013: le mthong bas bod kyi rgyal khams kyi mi tsam
NK035(ci)004:3014: gyis bstod pa legs so 'di'i dus na bi ma
NK035(ci)004:3015: las lo sum brgya bzhes pa lags rje blon rin
NK035(ci)004:3016: po che la de ltar mi mnga' yang gdul bya
NK035(ci)004:3017: la dgongs pa'o de ltar bi ma la dang sprul
NK035(ci)004:3018: pa'i rje blon gnyis mjal ba'i tshe sangs rgyas mya
NK035(ci)004:3019: ngan las 'das nas lo stong dang brgyad cu tham
NK035(ci)004:3020: pa lon pa lags so dus de tsam na bi
NK035(ci)004:3021: ma la mchod gnas dam par ni bzung pha rol
NK035(ci)004:3022: tu phyin pa dang dbu ma'i chos gsung zhing bzhugs
NK035(ci)004:3023: te bi ma la gro la bzhud pa'i bar du
NK035(ci)004:3024: sdud pa gsung ba'i khri'i rtsar sprang po gcig byung
NK035(ci)004:3025: ste des gzhan gyis ma tshor bar yi ge nyan
NK035(ci)004:3026: thos byis pa'i chos kyi sangs mi rgya pho rog
NK035(ci)004:3027: rdo rje 'gros kyi sa gzhi'i dal mi snyoms bya
NK035(ci)004:3028: ba'i tshig gnyis pa gcig bris pa 'dug nas de
NK035(ci)004:3029: nas bi ma las khri khar byon nas ka ba
NK035(ci)004:3030: li zhal phye bas yi ge mthong bas bi ma
NK035(ci)004:3031: la'i zhal nas 'dir su 'ongs gsungs so chos nyan
NK035(ci)004:3032: pa'i grwa pa de dag rnams na re su yang
NK035(ci)004:3033: ma byung zer ro khye'u gcig na re da ci
NK035(ci)004:3034: rtsa na sprang po rgad po gcig kor kor 'dug
NK035(ci)004:3035: pa yin zer bas bi ma la'i zhal nas sprang
NK035(ci)004:3036: po de tshol dang gsungs nas 'khor rnams kyis btsal
NK035(ci)004:3037: bas gling gseb kyi nyos chang ma gcig gi khyim
NK035(ci)004:3038: na 'dug nas khrid nas 'ongs te bi ma las
NK035(ci)004:3039: dris pas bdag ni pa gor bee ro tsa na'i
NK035(ci)004:3040: slob ma g.yu sgra snying po bya ba lags so
NK035(ci)004:3041: zer nas sems smad lnga la mkhas pa gcig 'dug
NK035(ci)004:3042: go de'i tshe bi ma las khong la dran pa
NK035(ci)004:3043: sems sde bcu gsum bstan pa dang g.yu'i sgra dang
NK035(ci)004:3044: lta ba mnyam sgom pa mnyam spyod pa mnyam ste
NK035(ci)004:3045: bya ma bu mnyam pa lta bur gyur nas snga
NK035(ci)004:3046: 'gyur dang phyi 'gyur zhes bya ba yang de tsam
NK035(ci)004:3047: na thos pa lags so de nas rje blon gyis
NK035(ci)004:3048: zhus te li gar ti'i skyems phra men gyi yol
NK035(ci)004:3049: go gang dang rta sngon po g.yu bya bya ba
NK035(ci)004:3050: la gser gyi sga srab dang zab chen gyi stan
NK035(ci)004:3051: dang g.yu'i thur dang kha gser kha g.yu dang bcas
NK035(ci)004:3052: phul nas chos 'ga' bsgyur bar zhu ba phul bas
NK035(ci)004:3053: bi ma la'i zhal nas rta dang gser gyis dgos
NK035(ci)004:3054: pa med chos ni sems can gyi don du bsgyur
NK035(ci)004:3055: na bdag gis ci rigs par bsgyur bar bya'o gsungs
NK035(ci)004:3056: nas dbu rtse rigs gsum gyi lho nub kyi mtshams
NK035(ci)004:3057: sgra bsgyur rgya gar gyi gling du pha rol phyin
NK035(ci)004:3058: pa dang rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba
NK035(ci)004:3059: dang dpal yang dag dang phur pa dang ma mo
NK035(ci)004:3060: dang gshin rje rnams ni phal cher gnyags dz+ny+aa na
NK035(ci)004:3061: ku m+aa ras bsgyur ro sems sde dang klong gi
NK035(ci)004:3062: man ngag 'ga' tsam yang bsgyur ro skor gsum gyi
NK035(ci)004:3063: rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga yang gnyags kyis bsgyur ro gsang
NK035(ci)004:3064: ba bla na med pa'i rgyud lung rnams ni gzhan
NK035(ci)004:3065: su la yang cha med par rje blon gsum gyi
NK035(ci)004:3066: thugs dam gyi mnogs chos su mdzad nas rigs gsum
NK035(ci)004:3067: bar khang du srod dang tho rangs bsgyur ro skor
NK035(ci)004:3068: gsum gyi rgyud lhag man ngag rnams kyang bsgyur ro
NK035(ci)004:3069: de ltar lo bcu'i bar la 'bras bu gsang sngags
NK035(ci)004:3070: kyi rgyud mang po bsgyur cing bzhugs so de nas
NK035(ci)004:3071: rje blon gyis bka' bsgros nas chos 'di ltar zab
NK035(ci)004:3072: pa ni sngon chad kyang ma byung phyis kyang bod
NK035(ci)004:3073: yul du mi 'byung bas 'di la tshul bzhin du
NK035(ci)004:3074: spyod pa mi 'byung bas phyi rabs kyi don du
NK035(ci)004:3075: sba bar bkas bcad do de nas bi ma las
NK035(ci)004:3076: mchims phu'i brag dmar dge gong du gsang ba bla
NK035(ci)004:3077: na med pa'i gsang ba snying thig gi po ti
NK035(ci)004:3078: rnams rgya'i dpe las bod kyi yi ger bsgyur nas
NK035(ci)004:3079: rgya nag po'i yul du 'gro bar thugs kyis dgongs
NK035(ci)004:3080: nas rje blon gnyis la yang ma gnang bar phyi
NK035(ci)004:3081: rabs kyi bstan pa'i btsal su sbas so thig skor
NK035(ci)004:3082: gsum gyi rgyud man ngag lhag chad med par rgya'i
NK035(ci)004:3083: dpe rnams ni phyi ma'i dus su chos 'di'i skor
NK035(ci)004:3084: gyi yi ge rnams tshong 'dus kyi 'o ma bzhin
NK035(ci)004:3085: bslad pa'i gang zag 'ga' 'byung bas de dag gi
NK035(ci)004:3086: gzhung dang man ngag rnams mi nyams par bya ba
NK035(ci)004:3087: la dgongs nas rgya dpe rnams sbas nas bzhugs so
NK035(ci)004:3088: der yang rje blon gyi thugs kyi rtog pa lo
NK035(ci)004:3089: gsum gyi bar la bcad nas rgya nag po'i yul
NK035(ci)004:3090: lci ba thub pa'i ri zhes bya ba la gshegs
NK035(ci)004:3091: te 'di'i dus na bi ma las lo sum brgya
NK035(ci)004:3092: dang bcu gsum bzhes pa lags so mkhas pa de
NK035(ci)004:3093: ni sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ji srid gnas pa'i
NK035(ci)004:3094: bar la 'gro ba mi'i lus su bzhugs pa lags
NK035(ci)004:3095: so lo brgya brgya la sprul pa re re bod
NK035(ci)004:3096: du snang bar byed do mkhas pa de ni sprul
NK035(ci)004:3097: pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rje dang zhal lan bdun
NK035(ci)004:3098: mjal zhing man ngag rnams kyi zhu tig mdzad do
NK035(ci)004:3099: de yang rgya gar gyi yul w+aa r+aa na s+ai'i
NK035(ci)004:3100: lho nub na ri bya rkang zhes bya ba la
NK035(ci)004:3101: lan lnga mjal lo rdo rje gdan du gnyis te
NK035(ci)004:3102: lan bdun mjal bas thig le mchog gi rgyud lung
NK035(ci)004:3103: man ngag rnams la yid ches so mkhas pa de
NK035(ci)004:3104: ni bstan pa mi gnas pa'i dus na rdo rje
NK035(ci)004:3105: gdan du lhag ma mi snang bar 'gyur ba yin
NK035(ci)004:3106: no +aa tsar+ya sa'i snying po ni mchims phur grongs
NK035(ci)004:3107: pas ltas bzang po byung ste bi ma la grongs
NK035(ci)004:3108: bya ba'i tha snyad byung ba yang de las byung
NK035(ci)004:3109: ba lags so des gang la brgyud na nyang ting
NK035(ci)004:3110: 'dzin bzang po la brgyud bi ma la rgya nag
NK035(ci)004:3111: tu bzhud nas lo lnga bcu rtsa lnga nas nyang
NK035(ci)004:3112: ting 'dzin bzang po de yang rang rgyud rnam par
NK035(ci)004:3113: dag nas rdo rje legs pas khams su ser ba
NK035(ci)004:3114: phab nas rnga mo'i kha lnga brgya byung ba la
NK035(ci)004:3115: nyang ting 'dzin bzang pos gser gyi rdo rje rtse
NK035(ci)004:3116: dgu pa gcig bar snang la 'phangs nas sngon gyi
NK035(ci)004:3117: dam tshig gis rjes su bskul te nyang la phul
NK035(ci)004:3118: nas de'i rdzas kyi zhwa'i lha khang zhes bya ba
NK035(ci)004:3119: bzhengs su gsol nas chos skyong la gnyer du gtad
NK035(ci)004:3120: do de lta bu'i mi ma yin gyi rdzas dang
NK035(ci)004:3121: longs spyod las bzhengs pa'i lha khang de'i nang na
NK035(ci)004:3122: bshad rgyud snying thig gi bka' rgyud dag ni skor
NK035(ci)004:3123: gsum ke'u tshang rim gsum du sbas so snyan brgyud
NK035(ci)004:3124: yi ge rigs kyi dpe rnams ni sgo khang gi
NK035(ci)004:3125: steng du shog dril rdza ma gang sbas so gsang
NK035(ci)004:3126: ba bla na med pa'i gser gyi snying po nyi
NK035(ci)004:3127: ma rab tu snang bar byed pa ka ba'i bsam
NK035(ci)004:3128: le'u gsum gyi khong seng la sbas te phyi rabs
NK035(ci)004:3129: kyi skal ldan gyi don du rgyas btab nas bar
NK035(ci)004:3130: der mi snang bar mdzad do snyan brgyud tshig gi
NK035(ci)004:3131: rim pa mchan du btab pa ni 'brom rin chen
NK035(ci)004:3132: 'bar ba la brgyud pa ni bka' srol mi nyams
NK035(ci)004:3133: par bya ba'i phyir brgyud pa'o //
NK035(ci)004:3134: bshad rgyud gsang ba 'i man ngag rnams gtsug lag
NK035(ci)004:3135: khang der lo brgyar gnas pa'i rting la 'brom rin
NK035(ci)004:3136: chen 'bar ba'i slob ma sbas blo gros dbang phyug
NK035(ci)004:3137: de'i slob ma dbu ru zhwa'i ldang ma dge mchog
NK035(ci)004:3138: gi bu gnas brtan ldang ma lhun gyi rgyal mtshan
NK035(ci)004:3139: zhes bya ba zhwa'i mgon po nyid kyis lung bstan
NK035(ci)004:3140: nas gsang ba'i rgyud lung man ngag 'di yod par
NK035(ci)004:3141: shes nas gtsug lag khang de'i gnyer nyang d+ha r+m+aa
NK035(ci)004:3142: r+aa dza zhes bya bas byed pa la gser gyi
NK035(ci)004:3143: chags pa mang por 'ong ba'i dod por gter rnams
NK035(ci)004:3144: 'byin du bcug nas lngang mas phyung ngo 'di'i dus
NK035(ci)004:3145: na sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas lo stong
NK035(ci)004:3146: sum brgya lnga bcu rtsa brgyad lon la lags so
NK035(ci)004:3147: ldang ma lhun gyi rgyal mtshan gyis gter 'di bton
NK035(ci)004:3148: nas lo bco lnga lon pa'i dus na myang ro'i
NK035(ci)004:3149: yul myang mtsho bya ba na lce thub pa'i dbang
NK035(ci)004:3150: po dang khyung mo bza' lags pa'i bu lce btsun
NK035(ci)004:3151: seng ge dbang phyug bya ba gcig yod de 'di'i
NK035(ci)004:3152: dus na snang khu yul snyan brgyud kyi gdams ngag
NK035(ci)004:3153: rigs mi 'dra ba bdun snang ngo de nas lo
NK035(ci)004:3154: gsum lon tsam na lngang ma lhun gyi rgyal mtshan
NK035(ci)004:3155: gyis bshad rgyud yang dag pa snying thig man ngag
NK035(ci)004:3156: 'di bstan cing bzhag pa'i gnas ma rnyed de lce
NK035(ci)004:3157: btsun mang yul du bzhud pa dang ldang ma man
NK035(ci)004:3158: ngag gi snod 'tshol gnyis gtsang gi ri gzar rgod
NK035(ci)004:3159: po lung du mjal nas sngar nas slob ma yin
NK035(ci)004:3160: pas gcig la gcig rab tu dgyes nas lngang mas
NK035(ci)004:3161: kyang man ngag bzhag pa'i snod lce btsun bzang bar
NK035(ci)004:3162: gzigs nas ldang ma'i zhal nas snga ma dang mi
NK035(ci)004:3163: 'dra ba'i snying thig gsang ba'i man ngag rnams khyod
NK035(ci)004:3164: la sbyin gyis 'o skol gnyis 'grogs la 'dongs zer
NK035(ci)004:3165: bas lce btsun gyi zhal nas bdag bla ma gcig
NK035(ci)004:3166: gi tshong la mchis pas de nas log pa dang
NK035(ci)004:3167: zhu 'tshal gsungs pa dang ldang ma'i zhal nas 'o
NK035(ci)004:3168: na dus nam tsam bya gsungs pas lce btsun gyi
NK035(ci)004:3169: zhal nas nya drug gi zla ba'i nya'i nyi ma
NK035(ci)004:3170: la kha rag rtsar bal po sgom chung bya ba
NK035(ci)004:3171: sgom chen shin tu bzang ba gcig yod par 'dug
NK035(ci)004:3172: pas de'i sar dus bagyi'o gsungs pas gnyis mthun nas
NK035(ci)004:3173: dus byas so de nas lce btsun gyis mang yul
NK035(ci)004:3174: nas log nas 'gro bar brtsams te ldang mas nya'i
NK035(ci)004:3175: nyi ma rang la byon bal po sgom chung na
NK035(ci)004:3176: so gzhon pa gcig gis sgom gyin 'dug pas ldang
NK035(ci)004:3177: mas jo bo de ltar byas pas sangs mi rgya
NK035(ci)004:3178: byas pas bal po na re jo bo thabs ji
NK035(ci)004:3179: lta bu yod gsungs so ldang ma'i zhal nas dpe
NK035(ci)004:3180: 'di la gzigs dang zhes lce btsun zhag gsum du
NK035(ci)004:3181: ma byung bas lta rtogs byas pas bal po yang
NK035(ci)004:3182: de gas grol ba lags so de nas tshes bco
NK035(ci)004:3183: brgyad kyi nyin mo lce btsun slebs nas byung bas
NK035(ci)004:3184: ldang ma'i zhal nas nga'i dpe 'di dag legs par
NK035(ci)004:3185: bris la cha bskyed ma bu'i yi ge rnams lhag
NK035(ci)004:3186: ma ma lus par bris la bshus nas khra'i zla
NK035(ci)004:3187: ba la skyol cig man ngag 'di rang gis shes
NK035(ci)004:3188: pa la gzhan la med gsungs nas de ltar byas
NK035(ci)004:3189: so de nas ldang ma dbu rur bzhud ldang ma
NK035(ci)004:3190: dang lce btsun mjal ba'i tshe sangs rgyas mya ngan
NK035(ci)004:3191: las 'das nas lo stong sum brgya dang brgyad cu
NK035(ci)004:3192: rtsa brgyad lon to lce btsun gyis gnubs yul rong
NK035(ci)004:3193: gi lang gro shug pa can du lang gro sma
NK035(ci)004:3194: ra can gyis dpe rnams bris so gsang ba bla
NK035(ci)004:3195: na med pa'i rgyud lung man ngag gi yi ge
NK035(ci)004:3196: rnams g.yas ban skyabs ses bris lhag ma 'o yug
NK035(ci)004:3197: lu mar dbyar chos kyi shes rab kyis bris skor
NK035(ci)004:3198: gsum gyi lhag ma rnams mtshur leg pa dang so
NK035(ci)004:3199: dpa' legs kyis bris so de nas dpe rnams tshar
NK035(ci)004:3200: nas zhu tig lan drug tu nyang dpal gyi 'byung
NK035(ci)004:3201: gnas dang gnyis kyis mdzad nas khra'i zla ba'i dus
NK035(ci)004:3202: su bum bcu gnyis gdum cig dang ltar tshe sum
NK035(ci)004:3203: cu rtsa lnga rta gsum khrab dgu khyer nas dpe
NK035(ci)004:3204: rnams skyel du byon pas dbu ru snye thang du
NK035(ci)004:3205: sleb tsa na btsun pa ldom bu ba cig na
NK035(ci)004:3206: re jo bo rdzas che gar 'gro zer lce btsun
NK035(ci)004:3207: gyis bdag ldang ma lhun gyi rgyal mtshan bya ba
NK035(ci)004:3208: sku drin can cig la zhabs tog skyel ba lags
NK035(ci)004:3209: byas pas btsun pa de na re ldang ma kha
NK035(ci)004:3210: sang bar gyi zla ba snga ma de'i nya la
NK035(ci)004:3211: sku gshegs nas gzhan rnams chos pa bzang po tsam
NK035(ci)004:3212: du mi byed par 'dug gnas brtan yin zer ba
NK035(ci)004:3213: la rtags bzang po ngo mtshar can mang po yang
NK035(ci)004:3214: byon 'chi ba'i dus kyang zin par gda' khyed la
NK035(ci)004:3215: khong gi gdams ngag bdog gam zer ro lce btsun
NK035(ci)004:3216: snyam pa bla ma grongs kyang rdzas 'di rnams 'dir
NK035(ci)004:3217: gnas gzhi yang 'dug pas 'dir tshogs gsog bya dgos
NK035(ci)004:3218: bla ma bsngosa pa yin pas bla ma'i don du
NK035(ci)004:3219: gtang bar bya snyam nas der gzhi phab bo der
NK035(ci)004:3220: btsun pa de na re bdag mal gro ba'i myang
NK035(ci)004:3221: bka' gdams bya ba yin pas ldang ma de gdams
NK035(ci)004:3222: pa che ba'i rtags su 'dug pas khyed la khong
NK035(ci)004:3223: gi gdams pa tshang bar bzhugs kyin gda' bas bdag
NK035(ci)004:3224: thugs la gdags par zhu zhes bya ba phul bas
NK035(ci)004:3225: lce btsun gyis kyang man ngag bstan du rung ba'i
NK035(ci)004:3226: snod du gzigs nas gsang ba'i man ngag sems lung
NK035(ci)004:3227: sgom khrid gnang ngo de rnams kyi rdzas dang yo
NK035(ci)004:3228: byad rnams dge 'dun snye thang ba dang dus de
NK035(ci)004:3229: tsam na thod pa lo ts+aa ba dang jo bo
NK035(ci)004:3230: 'brog mi lo ts+aa ba gnyis bzhugs pa la zhabs
NK035(ci)004:3231: tog mdzad do de nas lce btsun gyis gnubs yul
NK035(ci)004:3232: rong du byon myang bka' gdams pa bya ba de
NK035(ci)004:3233: ti sgro'i brag dkar po bya ba la sgom par
NK035(ci)004:3234: dam bcas nas sgom du song ngo dpon slob gnyis
NK035(ci)004:3235: kyis sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu sngon la sus thob
NK035(ci)004:3236: 'gran par byas nas gyes so de nas lce btsun
NK035(ci)004:3237: gyis dpa' gor rtsa nga lung dben rtsar byon no
NK035(ci)004:3238: lce btsun gyis man ngag gsang ba'i skor bzhi po
NK035(ci)004:3239: 'di dag bzhugs pa'i gnas 'tshol ba la lo bcu
NK035(ci)004:3240: lon pa'i bar du btsal bas ma rnyed de de
NK035(ci)004:3241: nas skor gsum gyi man ngag rgyud dang bcas pa
NK035(ci)004:3242: lang gro mchad pa stag 'dra'i mchad pa'i gong chu
NK035(ci)004:3243: mig 'og tu sbas nas klu btsan rdo rje bde
NK035(ci)004:3244: 'bar la gtad nas phyi rabs kyi skal ldan rnams
NK035(ci)004:3245: kyis rnyed par shog ces smon lam btab nas byi
NK035(ci)004:3246: ba lo'i dpyid zlar ba'i nya'i nyin mo sbas te
NK035(ci)004:3247: mi snang bar byas so de nas gsang ba bla
NK035(ci)004:3248: na med pa snying thig gi man ngag rnams lus
NK035(ci)004:3249: la bcangs nas yod de 'u yug gi nub ma'i
NK035(ci)004:3250: shug gseb na yod pa'i tshe mtshan mo'i rmi lam
NK035(ci)004:3251: na rgya gar ba sngo sangs shin tu 'jigs pa
NK035(ci)004:3252: gcig byung ste bdag ni bi ma la mi tra
NK035(ci)004:3253: mkhas pa ste skal ldan snying po'i yang bcud don
NK035(ci)004:3254: 'dod na mchims phu brag dmar dge gong yang ldebs
NK035(ci)004:3255: la gsang ba snying thig snying dang 'dra ba yod
NK035(ci)004:3256: kyi longs de dag khyer la 'u yug phyi gong
NK035(ci)004:3257: rdza yi ra ba ru sus kyang mthong ba med
NK035(ci)004:3258: par lo bdun sgoms des ni zag bcas phung po
NK035(ci)004:3259: mi snang ba yin no zhes lung bstan nas bdag
NK035(ci)004:3260: mchims phur 'gro ba'i bdogs byas nas zhag gsum lon
NK035(ci)004:3261: pa'i nyi ma 'char kar 'u yug phug steng gi
NK035(ci)004:3262: grog por mjal nas phyag dang bskor ba byas nas
NK035(ci)004:3263: 'u yug lung ba'i nags kyi dkyil du zla ba
NK035(ci)004:3264: phyed rje la gdams pa zhus nas zhun thar bcad
NK035(ci)004:3265: do dam pa'i zhal nas nga hor gyi yul du
NK035(ci)004:3266: 'gro bas hor gyi rgyal po lde mi tsan tra
NK035(ci)004:3267: bya ba gcig sems can dmyal ba'i gnas su 'gro
NK035(ci)004:3268: ba zhig yod pas de 'khor ba las sgrol bar
NK035(ci)004:3269: byed pas de'i bar byed pas de'i bar khyod nub
NK035(ci)004:3270: kyi ri la sdod la mchims phur ma 'gro gsungs
NK035(ci)004:3271: nas rje btsun rdzu 'phrul gyis gshegs so de nas
NK035(ci)004:3272: bdag gis nub tu lo gsum 'dug pa'i dus su
NK035(ci)004:3273: yang rje byon nas yang man ngag rnams la zhu
NK035(ci)004:3274: tig byas nas lhag ma ma lus par gnang ngo
NK035(ci)004:3275: de ltar res mjal res mi mjal bar lo bdun
NK035(ci)004:3276: du lhan cig mos gus byas so de nas dam
NK035(ci)004:3277: pa de li'i yul du mkha' 'gro ma brtse ba'i
NK035(ci)004:3278: rol pa zhes bya bas spyan drangs nas gshegs so
NK035(ci)004:3279: de nas lce btsun gyis mchims phur byon nas snying
NK035(ci)004:3280: tig man ngag btsal bas ma rnyed de de nas
NK035(ci)004:3281: zhag gsum gyi nyi ma phyed tsam na bud med
NK035(ci)004:3282: so dung so 'khor ma yod pa smin ma zangs
NK035(ci)004:3283: su 'dug pa dpral ba'i dkyil na gser gyi zla
NK035(ci)004:3284: phyed rdo rjes mtshan pa lag pa dang rkang pa
NK035(ci)004:3285: rnams bya chu bya'i sder mi ltar 'brel ba nu
NK035(ci)004:3286: ma las seng ge'i phru gu 'phyang ba zhig byung
NK035(ci)004:3287: nas 'o sngon gyi skal ldan man ngag gi bdag
NK035(ci)004:3288: po byung zer nas brag me long 'dra ba'i dkyil
NK035(ci)004:3289: nas po ti smug chung bton nas bdag la gtad
NK035(ci)004:3290: nas 'o yug phyi gong rdza'i ra bar song zhes
NK035(ci)004:3291: gsungs nas gtad do de nas log nas gnubs kyi
NK035(ci)004:3292: gseg ma lung du 'ongs nas lce btsun gyi dgongs
NK035(ci)004:3293: pa la bka' brgyud zab mo 'di kun la bzhag
NK035(ci)004:3294: pa'i gnas mi 'dug pas 'o yug nub ma'i brag
NK035(ci)004:3295: seng ge dang 'dra ba la sba'o snyam nas 'brug
NK035(ci)004:3296: lo'i dgun zla ra ba'i dus tshod ston ser kha
NK035(ci)004:3297: nyi ma byi ba'i nyi ma skar ma rgyal gyi
NK035(ci)004:3298: dus tshod nyi ma shar ba'i tshe gnam stong gi
NK035(ci)004:3299: nyin par rdo rje legs pa dang dpal sngags srung
NK035(ci)004:3300: gi bdag mo nag mo khros ma smug nag rag
NK035(ci)004:3301: gdong ma rnams la gtad nas phyi rabs kyi don
NK035(ci)004:3302: du smon lam btab nas mi snang bar mdzad do
NK035(ci)004:3303: de nas 'u yug gi phyi gong du snying thig
NK035(ci)004:3304: gsang ba'i man ngag gi po ti chung ba rnams
NK035(ci)004:3305: khyer nas sus kyang mthong ba med par lo bdun
NK035(ci)004:3306: nyams su blangs pas rig pa tshad la phebs nas
NK035(ci)004:3307: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba mthong ngo de nas
NK035(ci)004:3308: snying thig gsang ba'i po ti rnams byar gyi phu'i
NK035(ci)004:3309: brag dkar po theg pa dang 'dra bar sbas so
NK035(ci)004:3310: sngon gyi skor gsum gyi phyi mo rnams sle tshan
NK035(ci)004:3311: gsum gyi ri la sbas so yang dam pa dang
NK035(ci)004:3312: byar gyi phur lan cig mjal nas rgya nag po'i
NK035(ci)004:3313: yul du gshegs pas bdag gis mchims phur bskyal nas
NK035(ci)004:3314: dam pa rdzu 'phrul gyis gshegs so de nas lce
NK035(ci)004:3315: btsun gyis log nas rang bzhin du mi yul du
NK035(ci)004:3316: lo mang bzhugs nas shangs dang rta nag gi bar
NK035(ci)004:3317: gyi spo mthon ri nas slob dpon pad+ma'i chos dang
NK035(ci)004:3318: sgrub yig bton nas gtsang lung dben rtsar sbas so
NK035(ci)004:3319: cha lung gi khyi rtags dben rtsa nas sangs rgyas
NK035(ci)004:3320: ye shes rin po ches sbas ma thag pa'i gnubs
NK035(ci)004:3321: kyi ngan sngags brgya dang bcu bton nas gnubs kyi
NK035(ci)004:3322: phung po ri bo che la slar sbas so de
NK035(ci)004:3323: ltar dam pa dang lan gsum mjal snyan brgyud man
NK035(ci)004:3324: ngag rigs mi 'dra ba bdun mchan du btab bo
NK035(ci)004:3325: bka'i srol mi nyams pa'i phyir ro de ltar grub
NK035(ci)004:3326: pa thob nas kyang lo lnga bcu tham pa rong
NK035(ci)004:3327: dang byang phyi gong du bzhugs so grub pa ma
NK035(ci)004:3328: thob pa'i gong du lo bdun cu rtsa lnga ste
NK035(ci)004:3329: brgya dang nyer lnga na zag bcas mi snang bar
NK035(ci)004:3330: sku gshegs so zhal chems gsang ba'i gnad gsum bya
NK035(ci)004:3331: ba babs te de ni mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis
NK035(ci)004:3332: o rgyan gyi yul du spyan drangs te bsnams so
NK035(ci)004:3333: gong gi ti sgro la bsgoms pa'i myang bka' gdams
NK035(ci)004:3334: pa bya ba de yang bsgoms nas lo bco lnga
NK035(ci)004:3335: na rang rgyud rnam par dag nas zag pa zad
NK035(ci)004:3336: pa dang mngon par shes pa la sogs te yon
NK035(ci)004:3337: tan mang po byung nas de nas lo sum cu
NK035(ci)004:3338: rtsa gnyis na grongs nas nam mkha'i 'od dang sgra
NK035(ci)004:3339: dang sil snyan mang po grags pa la sogs pa
NK035(ci)004:3340: dang yul mi de kun gyi snang ba 'gyur nas
NK035(ci)004:3341: rang bzhin gyis bsam gtan la gnas pa yang byung
NK035(ci)004:3342: ngo rang gi snyan brgyud kyi gdams pa gnang ba'i
NK035(ci)004:3343: sgom chen pa 'ga' yang bsgoms pas mdze gsos pa
NK035(ci)004:3344: la sogs pa'i rtags bzang po byung ngo de ltar
NK035(ci)004:3345: lce btsun mi snang ba'i sar gshegs nas lo sum
NK035(ci)004:3346: cu na rong gi mnar mad'i lce sgom nag pos
NK035(ci)004:3347: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi bka' brgyud rnams bton
NK035(ci)004:3348: nas rang las gzhan la ma spel bar gdams pa'o
NK035(ci)004:3349: dbus gtsang du dar zhing rgyas par mdzad do lce
NK035(ci)004:3350: sgom gyis thon nas lo lnga bcu na bdag gis
NK035(ci)004:3351: gsang ba bla na med pa'i skor 'di rnams bton
NK035(ci)004:3352: nas rang las gzhan la ma spel bar gdams pa'o
NK035(ci)004:3353: 'di'i dus na sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas
NK035(ci)004:3354: lo stong lnga brgya dang drug cu rtsa brgyad lon
NK035(ci)004:3355: pa lags so de ltar bstan pa so so'i dar
NK035(ci)004:3356: nub dang 'phel 'grib ji ltar 'byung ba bdag po
NK035(ci)004:3357: gang gis byed par 'gyur ba la sogs pa tshe
NK035(ci)004:3358: lo bcu pa yan chad kyi babs so rnams yod
NK035(ci)004:3359: de 'dir yi ge mang gis dogs nas ma bris
NK035(ci)004:3360: so lo rgyus zhes bya ba lo du ma lon
NK035(ci)004:3361: pa'i rgyus da lta mthong ba dang 'dra bar gtan
NK035(ci)004:3362: la phebs pas na lo rgyus zhes bya'o de yang
NK035(ci)004:3363: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bsdus nas skyes
NK035(ci)004:3364: pa nas lo dpag tu med pas na de ltar
NK035(ci)004:3365: gyi yo ga'i lo rgyus yod pas na lo rgyus
NK035(ci)004:3366: kyi don no brgyud pa'i dgongs pa ni ras chod
NK035(ci)004:3367: dang gzu lum dang bsnan 'phri med pa dang man
NK035(ci)004:3368: ngag kha mi gcig gi sgro btags kyis bslad du
NK035(ci)004:3369: mi btub pas na yid ches pa'i dgos pa yod
NK035(ci)004:3370: do yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nas da
NK035(ci)004:3371: lta yan chod du tshig gis ma bslad cing gcig
NK035(ci)004:3372: thod tu gcig babs pas na brgyud pa'o dper na
NK035(ci)004:3373: dngos po'i rdzas lag tu brgyud pa'am rgyal po'i bka'
NK035(ci)004:3374: rtags lta bu'am rgyas btab pa'i rin po che la
NK035(ci)004:3375: skye 'bri mi btub pa lta bu'o de yang 'di
NK035(ci)004:3376: la byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa 'das rjes rgyud ma
NK035(ci)004:3377: chad pa dang tshig gi brgyud pa la bka' brgyud
NK035(ci)004:3378: zam ma chad pa dang don gyi brgyud pa la
NK035(ci)004:3379: mngon sum gyi gnad la yid dpyod kyis dpyad du
NK035(ci)004:3380: mi rnyed pas 'gyur med gsang chen gyi babs ma
NK035(ci)004:3381: chad pa dang bsod nams bsags pa'i brgyud pa gter
NK035(ci)004:3382: la longs spyod pa'i gang zag bar ma chad pa
NK035(ci)004:3383: mi yul du snang bar byas pa'o de'i phyir du
NK035(ci)004:3384: rab na yid ches pa'i gnad do lo rgyus chen
NK035(ci)004:3385: po zhes bya ba skal ldan gyi yid ches pa'i
